NG0200:88: dpal gyi chas bcus sku la spras pa /
NG0200:89: sangs rgyas thams cad kyi rje btsan du gyur pa /
NG0200:90: gar dgu'i tshul du bzhugs pa /
NG0200:91: yum khro mo gnam zhal ma /
NG0200:92: dbu dgu phyag bco brgyad ni /
NG0200:93: theg pa dgu dang stong pa bco brgyad yongs su rdzogs tshul du bzhugs pa /
NG0200:94: g.yas pa gtso bo la 'khyud pa /
NG0200:95: g.yon dung dmar gtso la stob pa /
NG0200:96: thabs shes rab yongs su rdzogs brdar /
NG0200:97: yab yum gnyis med du sbyor zhing */
NG0200:98: gzhal yas khang gdan dang bcas pa la /
NG0200:99: 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad yongs su rdzogs pa'i
NG0200:100: ngang las yab yum sbyor ba mdzad pa'i byang chub
NG0200:102: sprul sku'i khro bo 'chol pa phyogs bcur 'phros /

NG0200:115: de dag la yang so so'i sprul pa yang sprul sum sprul khro bo dang */
NG0200:117: pho brang dgu la gar dgu dang ldan pas khams
NG0200:118: gsum 'jigs byed dpal gyi chas yongs su rdzogs par
NG0200:119: yab yum gyi mkha' gsang las sprul te /

NG0200:126: gsang ba'i bdag po rdo rje chos kyis phyag dang bskor ba mdzad de /

NG0200:138: // rdo rje'i gad rgyangs bsgrags te stsol pa /

NG0200:372: sgo khyud ka brgyad rta babs rgyan sogs mdzes //
NG0200:373: a dkar gsal 'tsher zhi ba'i rten mthar thug / seng ge glang chen rta dang rma bya khyung *//
NG0200:374: rin chen khri rkang pad sdong bar du 'khyil //
NG0200:375: pad+ma zla ba nyi ma'i gdan steng gsal //
NG0200:376: mi bskyod mthing ga rdo rje dril bu 'dzin //
NG0200:377: snang mdzad dkarapo 'khor lo dril bu 'dzin //
NG0200:378: rin 'byung ser po nor bu dril bu 'dzin //
NG0200:379: mtha' yas dmar po pad+ma dril bu 'dzin //
NG0200:380: don grub ljang gu rgya gram dril bu 'dzin //
NG0200:381: kun kyang rdzogs skyil gnyis med yum chen ni //
NG0200:382: bzang mo spyan dang ma ma gos dkar sgrol //
NG0200:383: g.yas pa rigs 'dzin g.yon dril yab la 'khyud //
NG0200:384: kun bzang yid mthing rdo rje dril bu bsnams //
NG0200:385: bzang mo chos mthing mnyam gzhag phyag rgya gsal //
NG0200:386: sprul 'khor sa snying nam mkha'i snying po dang *//
NG0200:387: spyan ras gzigs dbang phyag na rdo rje ming *//
NG0200:388: la s+ye ma le girti nirti sring *//
NG0200:389: kun bzang byams pa sgrib sel 'jam dbyangs ming *//
NG0200:390: me tog bdud spros mar me dri chab sring *//
NG0200:391: lha dbang thags bzang shaka thub ser rab brtan //
NG0200:392: kha 'bar chos rgyal la sogs thub pa drug / gshin rje stobs chen rta mgrin bdud rtsi 'khyil //
NG0200:393: ro langs mi 'pham ral gcig khro gnyer yum //
NG0200:394: 'khor rnams nyi ma'i zer ltar rang bzhin 'du //
NG0200:395: rin chen rgyan rdzogs tshul dgu'i gar ldan mdzes //
NG0200:396: de las spro bsdu cho 'phrul cir yang bde /
NG0200:397: bde chen longs spyod rdzogs sku kun gyi rgyal //
NG0200:398: bsam gyis mi khyab bder 'dus rigs brgya yongs //
NG0200:399: rtsa ba lngar rdzogs de nyid kun rdzogs pa //
NG0200:400: gcig dang tha dad stong nyid snying rje bstan //
NG0200:401: bdag nyid rdo rje sems dpa' shel gyi mdog / rgyal ba'i spyi gzugs zhal @#//
NG0200:403: phyag g.yas rdo rje rtse lnga thugs kar bsnams //
NG0200:404: g.yon pas dngul dkar dril bu dku la brten //
NG0200:405: zhabs gnyis skyil krung nyi zla pad dkyil bzhugs //
NG0200:406: zhi tshul rgyan chas 'od zer sna tshogs 'bar //
NG0200:407: dung khang 'khor lo ljags pad thugs rdo rje //
NG0200:408: om dkar ahdmar hum mthing 'phro 'dur bzlas //
NG0200:409: gyen du bde gshegs sku gsung thugs mchod bskul //
NG0200:410: thur du snod bcud lus ngag yid sgrib sbyang *//
NG0200:411: tshur 'dus sku gsung thugs bcud dngos grub bsdu //
NG0200:412: rang sems rnam dag rdo rje sems dpa' yis //
NG0200:413: sku gsung thugs su bde bar gshegs par bstan //
NG0200:414: rgyud lung man ngag yongs rdzogs sgo nas bsgrub //
NG0200:415: dgra gsum bdud bzhi 'gro drug g.yang sa bcad //
NG0200:416: sum cu phrag drug gis 'grub las rnams 'grub //
NG0200:417: sku dang ye shes yongs rdzogs lhun gyis grub //
NG0200:418: rang bzhin zhi ba'i dkyil 'khor rnam bkod la //
NG0200:419: bde gshegs rgyal ba yongs gyis dbu rgyan no //
NG0200:420: de ltar phyogs bcu'i rgyal ba yongs rdzogs rnams //
NG0200:421: gdug pa 'dul phyir khro bo rol par bstan //
NG0200:422: rab tu gdul dka' khro zhing gtum pa la //
NG0200:423: zhi des lcug pas phan par mi 'gyur phyir //
NG0200:424: zhi tshogs dbu yi gtsug tu rab bsdus nas //
NG0200:425: bcom ldan de gshegs rgyal ba yongs rdzogs pa //
NG0200:426: rab 'jigs khro bo rol pa'i dkyil 'khor bstan //
NG0200:427: stong gsal rgyu las rang byung gzhal yas ni //
NG0200:428: chos dbyings mi 'gyur mthing nag gru gsum e //
NG0200:429: stobs chen g.yo byed ljang nag kha gdengs yam //
NG0200:430: thugs rje'i rlan gyis kun sdud dmar nag ra //
NG0200:431: rab brtan kun shong bcu gsum rdzogs byed sum //
NG0200:432: 'od gsal smin byed dngos 'joms dmar ser ram //
NG0200:433: rdo rje sra mkhregs rus pa'i ri rab stengs //
NG0200:434: phyi dang nang gsal rin chen yongs rdzogs b+h+rum //
NG0200:435: gzhal yas bkod pa tshad med rnam dag dbus //
NG0200:436: theg pa dgu rdzogs dpal chen dkyil 'khor dgu //
NG0200:437: 'khor 'das dbyer med ye shes sgo dgur gsal //
NG0200:438: ye shes lnga rdzogs rtsibs bzhi lte bar bcas //
NG0200:439: thugs rje'i zer ldan spros bral mu khyud mdzes //
NG0200:440: yon tan ma bkag rin chen zur brgyad ldan //
NG0200:441: mtshan nyid bzhi rdzogs gru chad rnam bzhis spras //
NG0200:442: de bzhin pho brang dgu la phrin las rdzogs //
NG0200:443: bdud 'joms ka bzhi chu srin gdan stengs btsugs //
NG0200:444: thabs shes nyi zla'i ka zhus zhing gdung btegs //
NG0200:445: thugs rjes gdal khyab ru tra'i lpags thog phub //
NG0200:446: sku gsum lhun grub thod tshar sum brtsegs la //
NG0200:447: gnam lcags rig rtsal gzer gyis rab tu bsdams //
NG0200:448: ye shes bzhi ldan zang thal nang sgo bzhi //
NG0200:449: ye shes zer lngas gling dgu'i bar mtshams bres //
NG0200:450: chags pa'i thugs rjes rak+ta'i zham chu 'bab //
NG0200:451: snying po'i don rtogs tsit+ta'i pho ltos brgyan //
NG0200:452: chos sku mnyam rdzogs bar khyams 'khor yug @#//
NG0200:454: dgos 'dod re skong rin chen sna lngas brtsigs //
NG0200:455: tshad med bzhi ldan sgo bzhi phyogs bzhir bgrad //
NG0200:456: rnam thar brgyad kyi them skas rim par brtan //
NG0200:457: thugs rjes 'dzin phyir chu srin ya them mdzes //
NG0200:458: 'byung po sri 'dul ma them rus sbal brjid //
NG0200:459: gdug pa tshar gcod sbrul nag skyes bu btsugs //
NG0200:460: 'khor ba rgyun gcod zhing lpags sgo logs bcad //
NG0200:461: chos kyi gan+di cong dang dril bu bsgrags //
NG0200:462: yul brgyad 'dzin bcom klu brgyad ka gdan stengs //
NG0200:463: tshogs brgyad rang dag lha brgyad ka bar btsugs //
NG0200:464: thabs shes brgyad ldan gza' brgyad ka zhur bskal //
NG0200:465: bcu drug rol pa'i zhing smug gdung chen bkram //
NG0200:466: 'gyu byed rang 'grol kun grol rgyu skar dral grab bkram //
NG0200:467: bzang ngan med mnyam zhing chen lpags thog bkram //
NG0200:468: ma rig mun sel nyi zla'i skar khung mdzes //
NG0200:469: 'khor 'das spyi chings chos sku'i bre bum pa //
NG0200:470: skyon gyis ma gos bum stan pad+mar gsal //
NG0200:471: sa lam yongs rdzogs 'khor 'degs 'khor lo brtsegs //
NG0200:472: kun khyab theg pa'i yongs rtser gdugs tog rngam //
NG0200:473: bstan pa'i spyi phud bya ru dar dpyangs brgyan //
NG0200:474: phrin las bzhi rdzogs rat+na'i rta babs brtsegs //
NG0200:475: chags bral pad stengs chos 'khor rab tu mdzes //
NG0200:476: rgya chad phyos su+u ma lhung zhing gdugs phub //
NG0200:477: rang byung mi nub mi mgo'i rin chen tog / rig stong dbyer med ri dwags chu srin mdzes //
NG0200:478: dbyings rig yongs 'brel sprin nag grib so gtibs //
NG0200:479: dbyings las rtsal shar sgo khang rgyan dgus mdzes //
NG0200:480: 'dod yon zhen med spyod phyir 'dod khyams bskor //
NG0200:481: dbyings nas kun snang mu tig thod ras spras //
NG0200:482: ma 'dres yongs rdzogs shel gyi mchod rten dkrigs //
NG0200:483: sna tshogs 'od gsal mchog phran da ru ka / ma rig sgrib sel bcu gcig rdo rje gseng *//
NG0200:484: thabs kyis sgrib sel zla phyed rdo rjes brgyan //
NG0200:485: bdud 'joms zhing drang lha chen rgyal mtshan brgyad //
NG0200:486: 'khor ba'i g.yul rgyal zhing chen 'phan brgyad phyar //
NG0200:487: don rtags brgyad ldan dur khrod brgyad kyis bskor //
NG0200:488: tshul bcu'i mtha' grol he ru'i gnas bcus gtams //
NG0200:489: khams gsum zil gnon rgya gram rwa bzhis mnan //
NG0200:490: ma chags phrin las kun khyab pad stong brdal //
NG0200:491: sangs rgyas stong rdzogs 'khor lo rtsibs stong phub //
NG0200:492: gsang sngags snying po 'gyur med brag ris gtams //
NG0200:493: gnyen pos mi shigs rdo rje'i ra bas bskor //
NG0200:494: gzung 'dzin nags sreg ye shes me lnga 'bar //
NG0200:495: byol song dregs pa nyi zla pad gdan brjid //
NG0200:496: dgos 'dod kun 'byung gter bum dpag bsam rgyas //
NG0200:497: snang srid yongs rdzogs gzhal yas khang chen gsal //
NG0200:498: phyi nang 'khor lo rin chen gsang ba e //
NG0200:499: zhi khro'i rgyan sogs dbye'am yongs rdzogs pa //
NG0200:500: gang la gang 'dul dkyil 'khor 'phrul shes bya //
NG0200:502: yas de dag rnal 'byor rang lus la //
NG0200:503: yongs rdzogs sgrub rten mchod rdzas dur khrod rdzogs //
NG0200:504: de yang rang rig sems kyi dkyil 'khor du //
NG0200:505: yongs rdzogs thig le nyag gcig ngo mtshar te //
NG0200:506: rgya chad phyogs lhung kun bral gzhal mtha' yas //
NG0200:507: dkyil 'khor yongs rdzogs kun gyi mthar thug yin //
NG0200:508: sgrub rdzas rten gyi rim pa mchod bcas ni //
NG0200:509: sku gsung thugs yon phrin las dmigs pa'i rten //
NG0200:510: sku rten gzugs la gsung rten snying po dgod //
NG0200:511: yon tan bdud rtsi phrin las phur pa bsham //
NG0200:512: sgos rten zhi ba mthar thug a dkar la //
NG0200:513: che mchog yongs rdzogs sgrub rten bum mthar thug / de bzhin yang dag me gcig gshin rje phram //
NG0200:514: pad+ma rta thod rta zhal phrin phur gcig / ma mo nal snying rig 'dzin sku gcig ma //
NG0200:515: dregs pa sku gcig drag sngags byang gcig ste //
NG0200:516: rten rnams yongs rdzogs sgrub rdzas rang lus yin //
NG0200:517: rig pa'i sems nyid sgrub rten kun mthar thug / 'dod yon rdzas 'jom phyi yi mchod pas te //
NG0200:518: rang lus rang byung bdud rtsi nang mchod rdzas //
NG0200:519: rtog tshogs rang byung rang grol gsang mchod de //
NG0200:520: yid chos dbyer med ngang dwangs mchod mthar thug / dkyil 'khor lte dbus zla kham e yi dkyil //
NG0200:521: chos dbyings a las rang byung lhun grub lha //
NG0200:522: kun bzang che mchog khro rgyal he ru ka / mthing nag zhal gsum phyag drug zhabs bzhi bgrad //
NG0200:523: g.yas dkar g.yon dmar dbus mthing bzhad gshe rngam //
NG0200:524: g.yas gsum rtse dgu rtse lnga rtse gsum bsnams //
NG0200:525: g.yon gsum b+han+da dung dmar thod khrag bsnams //
NG0200:526: rdo rje'i gsheg g.yas rin chen gshog g.yon gdengs //
NG0200:527: sku gsung thugs ldan srog gi ye shes gsal //
NG0200:528: dpal gyi chas bcu dur khrod rgyan yongs spras //
NG0200:529: zhabs bzhi dor stabs g.yas brkyangs g.yon bskums tshul //
NG0200:530: gnam zhal yum chen zhal gcig phyag gnyis mthing *//
NG0200:531: phyag g.yas rtse gsum gtsor khyud g.yon dmar stob //
NG0200:532: zhabs g.yas yab 'khril g.yon brkyang gtso la sbyor //
NG0200:533: rigs lngas dbu rgyan dur khrod rgyan drug gsol //
NG0200:534: gnyis med rab 'jigs me dpung klong na brjid //
NG0200:535: brdas bskul mkha' gsang rab sbyor sprul sras 'gyed //
NG0200:536: shar gyi rtsibs stengs rak+sha he ru ka / smug nag zhal gcig phyag gnyis 'khor lo g.yas //
NG0200:537: g.yon pa thod khrag zhabs gnyis brkyang bskum 'gyings //
NG0200:538: rak+sha kro ti shwa ri cha lugs yab 'dra 'khril //
NG0200:539: lho rtsibs g+hu ya he ru ka ser nag / zhal gcig phyag gnyis rin chen thod khrag bsnams //
NG0200:540: g+hu ya kro ti shwa ri yab 'dra 'khril //
NG0200:541: nub rtsibs bi shwa he ru ka dmar nag / zhal gcig phyag gnyis pad+ma thod khrag bsnams //
NG0200:542: bi shwa kro d+hi shwa ri yab 'dra 'khril //
NG0200:543: byang rtsibs yak+sha he ru ka ljang nag / zhal gcig phyag gnyis rgya gram thod @#//
NG0200:545: yak+sha kro d+hi shwa ri yab 'dra 'khril //
NG0200:546: dur khrod chas gsol brda rtags gtso dang 'dra //
NG0200:547: nyi dang zer bzhin sprul pa'i 'khor tshogs ni //
NG0200:548: phyogs skyong dregs 'dul khro bo chen po bcu //
NG0200:549: ta kr-ita sgo skyong pho nya bstan srung bcas //
NG0200:550: che mchog yon tan yongs rdzogs rang byung shar //
NG0200:551: phyogs mtshams pho brang brgyad du thugs kyi sras //
NG0200:552: dkyil 'khor shar dbus zla kham e yi dkyil //
NG0200:553: ru dra nyi zla pad+ma 'od 'bar steng *//
NG0200:554: bcom ldan thugs mchog badzra he ru ka / mthing nag zhal gsum phyag drug zhabs bzhi bgrad //
NG0200:555: g.yas dkar g.yon dmar dbus mthing bzhad rngam gshe //
NG0200:556: g.yas gsum rdo rje kha t+wam rnge chung bsnams //
NG0200:557: g.yon gsum dril bu b+han dmar rgyu zhags bsnams //
NG0200:558: gshog gnyis zhabs bzhi brkyangs bskums dor stabs tshul //
NG0200:559: sku gsung thugs srog dur khrod chas rnams rdzogs //
NG0200:560: kro d+hi shwa ri yum chen sku la 'khril //
NG0200:561: phyag zhabs chas sogs brdas bskul gtso dang 'dra //
NG0200:562: shar gyi rtsibs stengs bud+d+ha he ru ka / smug nag g.yas pa rdo rje g.yon rgyu zhags /
NG0200:563: bud+d+ha kro d+hi g.yas 'khyud g.yon dmar stob //
NG0200:564: lho yi rtsibs steng rat+na he ru ka / ser nag g.yas g.yon rat+na stong gsum bsnams //
NG0200:565: rat+na kro ti g.yas 'khyud g.yon dmar stob //
NG0200:566: nub tu rtsibs steng pad+ma he hu ka / dmar nag g.yas pa pad+ma ti ra bsnams //
NG0200:567: pad+ma kro d+hi g.yas 'khyud g.yon dmar stob //
NG0200:568: byang gi rtsibs stengs karma he ru ka / ljang nag g.yas g.yon rgya gram ri rab bsnams //
NG0200:569: karma kro d+hi g.yas 'khyud g.yon dmar stob //
NG0200:570: sprul 'khor kau ri ma brgyad sid+ha brgyad //
NG0200:571: sgo skyong bka' srung yang dag thugs rdzogs shar //
NG0200:572: dkyil 'khor lho dbus zla kham e yi dkyil //
NG0200:573: chu glang nyi zla pad+ma 'od 'bar steng *//
NG0200:574: bcom ldan sku mchog 'jam dpal gshin rje gshed //
NG0200:575: mthing nag zhal gsum phyag drug zhabs bzhi bgrad //
NG0200:576: g.yas dkar g.yon dmar dbus mthing bzhad gshe rngam //
NG0200:577: g.yas gsum 'khor lo ral gri dgra s+t+wa bsnams //
NG0200:578: g.yon gsum sdig mdzub mdung dang b+han dmar bsnams //
NG0200:579: gshog gnyis zhabs bzhi brkyangs bskums dor stabs bgrad //
NG0200:580: sku gsung thugs srog dur khrod chas rnams rdzogs //
NG0200:581: sbyor yum be ta li ni sku la 'khril //
NG0200:582: sgrol yum tsa ti tri shul b+han dmar bsnams //
NG0200:583: phyag zhabs chas rdzogs brdas bskul gtso dang 'dra //
NG0200:584: shar rtsibs gsod byed ya ma ra dza mthing *//
NG0200:585: g.yas pa 'khor lo g.yon pa dgra s+t+wa bsnams //
NG0200:586: nag mo ral gcig g.yas 'khyud g.yon dmar stob //
NG0200:587: lho rtsibs myos byed 'bar ba ser nag la //
NG0200:588: g.yas pa be con g.yon pa dgra s+t+wa bsnams //
NG0200:589: gtum mo dug hrul g.yas 'khyud g.yon dmar stob //
NG0200:590: nub rtsibs ar+ya me ru tse dmar po //
NG0200:591: g.yas pa dung khrag g.yon pa dbyug to bsnams //
NG0200:593: zer can ma g.yas 'khyud g.yon dmar stob /
NG0200:594: byang rtsibs ral pa tshar dgu ljang nag la //
NG0200:595: g.yas pa gtun shing g.yon pa dung dmar bsnams //
NG0200:596: nag mo re ti g.yas 'khyud g.yon dmar stob //
NG0200:597: sprul 'khor phyogs skyong chen po bcu gnyis dang *//
NG0200:598: sgo skyong bka' srung 'jam dpal sku rdzogs shar //
NG0200:599: dkyil 'khor nub dbus zla gam e yi dkyil //
NG0200:600: klu brgyad nyi zla pad+ma 'od 'bar steng *//
NG0200:601: bcom ldan gsung mchog pad+ma dbang chen sku //
NG0200:602: dmar nag zhal gsum phyag drug zhabs bzhi bgrad //
NG0200:603: g.yas dkar g.yon sngo dbus dmar bzhad gshe rngam //
NG0200:604: g.yas gsum rdo rje kha t+wam sbrul zhags bsnams //
NG0200:605: g.yon gsum dril chen b+han dmar lcags sgrog bsnams //
NG0200:606: gshog gnyis zhabs bzhi brkyangs bskums dor stabs tshul //
NG0200:607: sku gsung thugs srog dur khrod chas kun rdzogs //
NG0200:608: pad+ma gzi ldan bde chen yum mchog 'khril //
NG0200:609: phyag zhabs chas rdzogs brdas bskul gtso dang 'dra //
NG0200:610: shar rtsibs steng du rdo rje dbang chen dkar //
NG0200:611: g.yas pa rdo rje g.yon pa thod khrag bsnams //
NG0200:612: rdo rje dbang phyug g.yas 'khyud g.yon dmar stob //
NG0200:613: lho rtsibs steng du rin chen dbang chen ser //
NG0200:614: g.yas pa rin chen g.yon pa thod khrag bsnams //
NG0200:615: rat+na dbang phyug g.yas 'khyud g.yon dmar stob //
NG0200:616: nub rtsibs steng du pad+ma dbang chen dmar //
NG0200:617: g.yas pa pad dkar g.yon pa thod khrag bsnams //
NG0200:618: pad+ma dbang phyug g.yas 'khyud g.yon khrag stob //
NG0200:619: byang rtsibs steng du karma dbang chen ljang *//
NG0200:620: g.yas pa rgya gram g.yon pa thod khrag bsnams //
NG0200:621: karma dbang phyug g.yas 'khyud g.yon dmar stob //
NG0200:622: sprul 'khor zil gnon khro bo yab yum brgyad //
NG0200:623: sgo skyong bka' srung pad+ma gsung rdzogs shar //
NG0200:624: dkyil 'khor byang dbus zla gam e yi dbus //
NG0200:625: lha chen nyi zla pad+ma 'od 'bar stengs //
NG0200:626: bcom ldan las mchog rdo rje gzhon nu'i sku //
NG0200:627: mthing nag zhal gsum phyag drug zhabs bzhi bgrad //
NG0200:628: g.yas dkar g.yon dmar dbus mthing bzhad gshe rngam //
NG0200:629: g.yas g.yon dang po rtse dgu me dpung bsnams //
NG0200:630: bar gnyis rtse lnga kha t+wam mthar phur 'dril //
NG0200:631: gshog gnyis zhabs bzhi brkyangs bskums dor stabs tshul //
NG0200:632: sku gsung thugs srog dur khrod chas rnams rdzogs //
NG0200:633: 'khor lo rgyab 'debs yum chen sku la 'khril //
NG0200:634: phyag zhabs chas sogs brdas bskul gtso dang 'dra //
NG0200:635: shar rtsibs sras mchog bud+d+ha ki la dkar //
NG0200:636: g.yas pa phur pa g.yon pa thod khrag bsnams //
NG0200:637: yum gcig sangs rgyas g.yas 'khyud g.yon dmar stob //
NG0200:638: lho rtsibs sras mchog rat+na ki la ser //
NG0200:639: g.yas pa dgra s+t+wa g.yon pa thod khrag bsnams //
NG0200:640: yum chen rin chen g.yas 'khyud g.yon dmar stob //
NG0200:641: nub rtsibs sras mchog pad+ma ki la dmar //
NG0200:642: g.yas pa gri gug g.yon pa thod khrag @#//
NG0200:644: yum gcig pad+ma g.yas 'khyud g.yon dmar stob //
NG0200:645: byang rtsibs sras mchog karma ki la ljang *//
NG0200:646: g.yas pa mdung thung g.yon pa thod khrag bsnams //
NG0200:647: yum gcig las byed g.yas 'khyud g.yon dmar stob //
NG0200:648: sprul 'khor khro bcu yab yum za gsod bcas //
NG0200:649: sgo skyong bka' srung phrin las phur tshogs shar //
NG0200:650: shar lho'i dkyil 'khor zla gam e dbus su //
NG0200:651: ma mo nyi zla pad+ma 'od 'bar steng *//
NG0200:652: dpal chen bla med gsang ba mngon rdzogs sku //
NG0200:653: mthing nag zhal gsum phyag drug zhabs bzhi bgrad //
NG0200:654: g.yas dkar g.yon dmar dbus mthing brjid dang ldan //
NG0200:655: g.yas gsum rdo rje khyung khra sbrul zhags bsnams //
NG0200:656: g.yon gsum b+han dmar zhing dbyug dung chen bsnams //
NG0200:657: kun bzang nyid bzhi bde mchog sku la 'khril //
NG0200:658: g.yas pa dril bu gtso 'khyud g.yon dmar stob //
NG0200:659: yab yum sku la dur khrod chas rnams rdzogs //

NG0200:1042: bla med he ru'i gsung mtha' sum cu pa /
NG0200:1043: rigs 'dzin gsung mtha' yi ge bcu par thug /
NG0200:1044: de bzhin dregs pa kun 'dul gsung mtha' 'bru bcu
NG0200:1045: pa // stobs ldan nag po'i gsung mtha' yi ge brgyad //
NG0200:1046: zhi khro yongs dril sngags mtha' don brgyad yin //
NG0200:1047: khro rgyal yongs rdzogs drag sngags so lngar 'dus //
NG0200:1048: de nyid gsung srog yi ge hum la rdzogs //
NG0200:1049: gsung gi rang bzhin shes pas gsung mtha' thug / bde gshegs ma lus yongs rdzogs dgongs pa'i mtha' //
NG0200:1050: bye brag dang ni yongs rdzogs yang dag bshad /
NG0200:1051: ma rig 'ching bzlog 'chi bdag bdud chen po //
NG0200:1052: kun gzhi ye shes snying po rtogs nas sangs //
NG0200:1053: ma bcos spros med ngang dngas lhug par zhog / snang srid khram 'debs gshin rje gshed dgongs yin //
NG0200:1054: 'khor 'das snang stong dbyer med rta skad gsum //
NG0200:1055: rang sems dri med rnam dag sa lam bcad //
NG0200:1056: snang stong dran stong grag stong so mar zhog / 'khor 'das zil gnon rta skad dgongs pa yin //
NG0200:1057: chos kun sems su yang dag gnas lugs te //
NG0200:1058: rang bzhin rnal 'byor spros bral sku gsum rdzogs //
NG0200:1059: ma bkag rang 'byung ma 'breng rang zhir zhog / gzung 'dzin mun gsal me gcig dgongs pa yin //
NG0200:1060: ma rig rnam rtog nyon mongs dug mtsho'i nang *//
NG0200:1061: rang byung ye shes rtsi bcud thig les gzhom //
NG0200:1062: ma spangs mi gnas 'dod yon rnam dag zhog / bdud rtsi 'chi med dgongs pa mthar thug yin //
NG0200:1063: nga bdag gzung 'dzin dgra bgegs ling+ga la //
NG0200:1064: rang rig ye shes phur pas khyab par gdab //
NG0200:1065: rtogs pa thal phyung gsum mtha' gcig tu bzhag / phur pa thal phyin dgongs pa chen po yin //
NG0200:1066: ma gcig kun gzhi kun tu bzang mo la //
NG0200:1067: snying po rig pa'i ye shes thams cad mkhyen //
NG0200:1068: ma nor ma bcos kun khyab ma bslab zhog / kun khyab ma chen dgongs pa'i mthar thug yin //
NG0200:1069: thabs shes kun ldan ye stong bdag nyid rig / mi bsgom ma yengs rig pa dbyings su 'dzin //
NG0200:1070: brjod med shes rab g.yo med rang grol zhog / rig 'dzin rang grol dgongs pa chen po yin //
NG0200:1071: 'khor 'das chos kun ye grol pha mtha' yas //
NG0200:1072: 'dzin med rang grol gza' gtad 'khrul pa zhig /
NG0200:1073: lha 'dre rang snang rang grol chen por zhog /
NG0200:1074: 'jig rten kun grol dgongs pa mthar thug yin //
NG0200:1075: srid rtsa nyes rgyu ha la bdag rtog dug / rtsa bral snying po'i sngags kyis dug rang bsad //
NG0200:1076: dug lnga ye shes lnga ru rang grol bzhag / dug lnga rang @#//
NG0200:1077: gshed mtha' bral dgongs pa yin //
NG0200:1078: de dag yongs rdzogs sems nyid chos kyi sku //
NG0200:1079: snang srid gzhir bzhengs 'khor 'das dbyer med rdzogs //
NG0200:1080: gsang ba bla med byang chub snying pos khyab //
NG0200:1081: 'khor 'das dbyer med thig le nyag gcig las //
NG0200:1082: ma 'gags rol pa sna tshogs rtsis gdab bral //
NG0200:1083: rang bzhin med grol skye med dbyings su dag / ma 'dres yongs rdzogs rang byung ye shes dang *//
NG0200:1084: bde gshegs dgongs pa rtsis gdab brjod med rdzogs //
NG0200:1085: sku gsung thugs mtha' khog dkrul spros bcad nas //
NG0200:1086: rnal 'byor blo mthun bsgrub lugs rtsa lag gnyis //
NG0200:1087: 'di ni yongs rdzogs bsgrub chen drel ba dang *//
NG0200:1088: zhi khro rkyang dang sku gsum yang dril las //
NG0200:1089: yan lag sngags bsgrub brgyad las 'dir ma smos //
NG0200:1090: 'di dag spros bcas spros chung shin tu chung *//
NG0200:1091: sangs rgyas bstan bsrung ched gnyer don du bstan //
NG0200:1092: mdor na ngas bstan rgyud lung thams cad du //
NG0200:1093: bde gshegs 'dus dang yongs rdzogs kun dril dang *//
NG0200:1094: kun rig kun gsal kun chub gsang 'dus sogs //
NG0200:1095: sna tshogs phun sum thams cad ma lus sgra //
NG0200:1096: thugs dgongs lhad med rgyud der mtshon tshig las /
NG0200:1097: ming phyogs blo mthas phyogs ris ltos mi bya //
NG0200:1098: sgyu ma smig rgyu rmi lam gzugs brnyan dang *//
NG0200:1099: dri za'i grong khyer brag cha chu zla dang *//
NG0200:1100: chu sbur dmigs rkyen sprul pa la sogs te //
NG0200:1101: shes bya bcu tshul gsang sngags nyams su blangs //
NG0200:1102: dkrugs bcus gab stsogs ras chod bzlog phyir ston //
NG0200:1103: ngas sprul phyi rabs rig 'dzin dam pas bsdeb //
NG0200:1104: man ngag dbang thob gdeng ldan rnal 'byor pas //
NG0200:1105: yid 'ong dben pa'i bsgrub gnas su //
NG0200:1106: man+dal phyi nang mchod pa bsham //
NG0200:1107: yan lag bcu yis tshogs chen bsag / gzhan yang sta gon ci rigs bya /
NG0200:1108: phyi nang gsang ba'i mtshams bsdams te //
NG0200:1109: gnas dang mtshams kyi dkyil 'khor bzhengs //
NG0200:1110: bdud rtsi lnga yis chag chag gdab //
NG0200:1111: thig tshon grub chen skabs dang mtshungs //
NG0200:1112: bri thabs dbus mthing gru gsum la //
NG0200:1113: zla gam gnam sgo thod zlum bskor //
NG0200:1114: gru chad sgo khyud yongs rdzogs bri //
NG0200:1115: de dbus rat+na rdza'i bum pa //
NG0200:1116: bre tshad nang du rnam rgyal dang *//
NG0200:1117: a mr-i ta yi ril bus dgang */
NG0200:1118: kha rgyan gzungs thag rgyan gyis spras //
NG0200:1119: de steng mtshan ldan ka pa la //
NG0200:1120: dpal chen gris sku dmigs pa'i rten //
NG0200:1121: lcags phur mtshan ldan khro zhal can //
NG0200:1122: gu gul gyis bdug dar gyis spras //
NG0200:1123: dpal chen skur bskyed e la gzug / sman rag gtor chen la sogs pa //
NG0200:1124: phyi nang gsang ba'i mchod pas bskor //
NG0200:1125: mtshams gcad sgo dbye brda' phyag 'tshal //
NG0200:1126: byin dbab dam bshags mchod rdzas dbul //
NG0200:1127: de ltar las bdun yongs rdzogs nas //
NG0200:1128: khyad par phrin las de bzhin nyid //
NG0200:1129: kun snang rgyu las 'byung rim brtseg / gzhal yas gdan bskyed rgyu hum @#//
NG0200:1131: bdag nyid che mchog he ru ka / mthing nag zhal gsum phyag drug pa //
NG0200:1132: g.yas gyi phyag gsum rdo rje la //
NG0200:1133: g.yon gyi phyag gsum b+han dmar bsnams /
NG0200:1134: zhabs bzhi brkyangs bskums dor thabs bgrad //
NG0200:1135: rdo rje rin chen gshog pa gdengs //
NG0200:1136: dur khrod chas rdzogs yum chen mo //
NG0200:1137: gnam zhal zhal gcig phyag gnyis 'khril //
NG0200:1138: g.yas pa kha t+wam g.yon dung dmar //
NG0200:1139: sku mdog rgyan rnams yab dang mtshungs //
NG0200:1140: kun gyi bdag nyid rtsa ba'i lha'o //
NG0200:1141: dpal gyi spyi gtsug mgrin pa dang *//
NG0200:1142: thugs ka lte ba 'khor lo bzhir //
NG0200:1143: 'jam dpal spyan ras gzigs dbang dang *//
NG0200:1144: rdo rje sems dpa' rig pa'i bdag / rim pa bzhin bsgom rigs lnga yis //
NG0200:1145: dbu la brgyan te yan lag lha'o //
NG0200:1146: de nas sras mchog go cha'i lha //
NG0200:1147: dpral bar 'jam dpal gshin rje gshed //
NG0200:1148: mgrin par rta mgrin dbang gi lha //
NG0200:1149: thugs kar badzra he ru ka / lte bar rdo rje gzhon nu che /
NG0200:1150: gsang bar bla med he ru ka / spyi bor rig 'dzin 'dus pa'i sku //
NG0200:1151: zhabs kyi pus mo g.yas g.yon steng *//
NG0200:1152: dregs pa kun 'dul chen po dang *//
NG0200:1153: 'jigs byed stobs ldan nag po bskyed //
NG0200:1154: rdo rje rin chen gshog dpung rtser //
NG0200:1155: klu 'dul khyung chen dkar nag bskyed //
NG0200:1156: so so'i 'khor tshogs khro bo dang *//
NG0200:1157: khro mo yang sprul sum sprul bcas //
NG0200:1158: 'bar khro rngam brjid gsal brtan nas //
NG0200:1159: byin brlab dbang bskur spyan drang bstim //
NG0200:1160: mchod bstod tshogs 'khor dus bzhir dbul //
NG0200:1161: de dag sems kyi cho 'phrul te //
NG0200:1162: rang bzhin skye med chos kyi sku //
NG0200:1163: lha nyid snang stong gnyis su med //
NG0200:1164: rol pa ma 'gag longs spyod sku //
NG0200:1166: phrin las longs spyod sprul pa'i sku //
NG0200:1167: sku gsum rang la ngo sprad nas //
NG0200:1169: bdud bzhi gzhom dang dgra gsum bsad //
NG0200:1170: 'gro drug g.yang sa gcad bya'i phyir //
NG0200:1171: srog snying rdzong dang 'phrad gnad kyis //
NG0200:1172: yang dag nges don rab ldan pas //
NG0200:1173: snang stong grag stong bde stong gi / ngang la bying rgod gnyis spangs te //
NG0200:1174: kun gyi gsang srog hum gi bsnyen //
NG0200:1175: 'dzab bstod dbyangs bcas rig rtsal sbyang *//
NG0200:1176: de nas bde gshegs yongs rdzogs pa'i //
NG0200:1177: gsang sngags 'dus pa nye bar bsten //
NG0200:1180: om badzra shri ma ha kro d+ha /
NG0200:1181: om shri he ru ka ya man+ta ka / hrihpad+man+ta kr-ita /
NG0200:1182: hum badzra ki li ki la ya /
NG0200:1189: ma ma kro d+hi shwa ri /
NG0200:1191: dz+wa la ram ram hum hum phat phat /
NG0200:1193: mgar gyi tsha tsha lta bur bzlas //
NG0200:1194: thun mtshams bstod cing phrin las bcol //
NG0200:1195: smon lam btab cing rdzogs rim bsgom //
NG0200:1196: grangs 'bum bsnyen cing rtags la sbyar //
NG0200:1200: rmi lam mgo la nyi ma shar //
NG0200:1201: mchod rten rtse la sdod pa dang *//
NG0200:1202: bud med tshogs 'dus bsnyen bkur byed //
NG0200:1203: lus bde ngag nus sems rtogs 'char //
NG0200:1204: bum pa'i rdzas la dngos grub blang *//
NG0200:1205: rgyun du za tshogs drang zhing rten //
NG0200:1206: bde gshegs gcig grub kun gyi ngang *//
NG0200:1207: de bzhin bsgrub chos las sbyor stsogs //
NG0200:1208: gsang sngags rgyud sde bsam yas kyi //
NG0200:1209: las sbyor la sogs gang dang gang *//
NG0200:1210: gang la brtsams kyang the tshom med //
NG0200:1211: dkyil 'khor bsdus te rgyun spyod bya //
NG0200:1212: zhi khro yongs rdzogs bsnyen bsgrub 'dir //
NG0200:1213: dus gsum bde gshegs gsang ba 'dus //
NG0200:1214: bdag gzhan yongs kyi dpal chen po //
NG0200:1215: mchog gi dam pa 'di bsgrubs pas //
NG0200:1216: bdag srung rtsa ba'i bsnyen pa'o //
NG0200:1218: dpal gsang ba 'dus pa rgyud kyi rgyal po las /
NG0200:1219: zhi khro yongs rdzogs 'dus pa'i bsnyen bsgrub gzhi bstan
NG0200:1220: pa'i le'u ste brgyad pa'o // // de nas 'dus
NG0200:1222: ston pa kun tu bzang po dpal che mchog he ru ka la gsol pa //
NG0200:1224: tshogs kyi slob dpon kun tu bzang *//
NG0200:1225: tshogs rje tshogs bdag he ru ka / rgyud don yongs rdzogs bsgrub chen po //
NG0200:1226: bdag cag 'khor la bka' stsal zhu //
NG0200:1227: de skad gsol par thugs dgongs te //
NG0200:1228: ston pa chen pos bka' stsal pa //
NG0200:1230: bde gshegs zhi khro yongs rdzogs pa'i //
NG0200:1231: rgyud don gsang ba'i bsgrub chen la //
NG0200:1232: bzhi ste phun sum tshogs gzhi bzung *//
NG0200:1233: sta gon rim pas sgrom du gzhug / dngos gzhi bsnyen sgrub gzhung bsrangs te //
NG0200:1234: mtha' rgyas cho gas rjes bskyang ngo *//
NG0200:1235: bsgrub gzhi phun sum tshogs bdun dpyad //
NG0200:1236: bsgrub rkyen bla ma phun tshogs ni //
NG0200:1237: bde gshegs bka' babs bsgrub rgyud zin //
NG0200:1238: dbang rnams yongs rdzogs dam la gnas //
NG0200:1239: blta bas thag chod ting 'dzin gsal //
NG0200:1240: spyod pa blang dor man ngag can //
NG0200:1241: gsang sngags mtha' drug rdzogs pa la //
NG0200:1242: thos pas rgyud grol snying rje yis //
NG0200:1244: sgrub rten slob ma phun tshogs ni //
NG0200:1245: dam gtsang dpa' brtan snying rus che //
NG0200:1246: blo che shes rab mchog tu bzang *//
NG0200:1247: bsgrub dang phrin las brtson 'grus can //
NG0200:1248: bzo mkhas rig gsal dad ldan gces //
NG0200:1249: bsgrub gnas phun sum tshogs pa ni //
NG0200:1250: bkra shis gangs rgyud ri bzangs 'dab //
NG0200:1252: sngon yang grub thob rkyen thub par //
NG0200:1253: bsgrub khang pho brang lta bur brtsig / bsgrub pa'i grogs 'khor phun tshogs ni //
NG0200:1254: rgyud zhi sha tsha blo gsal zhing *//
NG0200:1255: mi bslu gsang thub nga lo yang *//
NG0200:1257: las brgya mdzes sdug yid 'ong ba //
NG0200:1258: rigs dang mtshan ldan 'dris thub rten //
NG0200:1261: rten rdzas mchod rdzas dngos grub rdzas //
NG0200:1262: 'cho ba zas dang rkyen zlog sman //
NG0200:1263: sna tshogs re skong yo byad sogs //
NG0200:1264: bsgrub pa'i dus tshod phun tshogs ni //
NG0200:1265: spyir na lo zla gza' skar dang *//
NG0200:1266: zhag dus dar dang yar ngo gces //
NG0200:1267: bye brag zhi rgyas dbang drag gam //
NG0200:1268: bsnyen bsgrub las sbyor dus kun brtsi //
NG0200:1269: sgrub chos phun sum tshogs pa ni //
NG0200:1270: ma ha'i rgyud dang a nu'i lung *//
NG0200:1271: a ti man ngag skor la sogs //
NG0200:1272: shes bya kun la mkhas par sbyang *//
NG0200:1273: mdor na bde gshegs gsang 'dus pa'i //
NG0200:1275: sgrom 'jug sta gon rim pa bcas //
NG0200:1276: sa brtag gzung sbyang dkyil 'khor brtsig / spyi bshags bskang bya phyi mtshams bcad //
NG0200:1277: sri mnan sgo srung byang bu gdags //
NG0200:1278: ma tram mnan cing phyin gyis brlab //
NG0200:1279: sgrub rdzas byin brlab chag chag gdab //
NG0200:1280: thig gdab sa tshon byin gyis brlab //
NG0200:1281: gzugs brnyan dkyil 'khor bri bya ste //
NG0200:1282: thig bzhi btab pas ling tshe dgu'i //
NG0200:1283: kha dog phyogs mtshon thod pa brtsig / dbus nas brtsams te ling tshe dgu'i //
NG0200:1284: zla gam sgo gcig e dgus mtshon //
NG0200:1285: sgo sgor 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi bar //
NG0200:1286: mu khyud dang bcas re re dgod //
NG0200:1287: kun la rin chen zur brgyad de //
NG0200:1288: mdo mtshams ka bzhi sgo zang thal //
NG0200:1289: spros la dga' na sgo rdzogs pa //
NG0200:1290: kun tu dgu ru mdzes par bri //
NG0200:1291: kun gyi phyi ru khyams sgo bzhi //
NG0200:1292: pho nya reg mthing dkar ser leb ljang *//
NG0200:1293: 'dod yon pha gu dra ba dang *//
NG0200:1294: phra phyed mda' yab de ru ka / ka brgyad rta babs chos 'khor sogs //
NG0200:1295: zhi khro yongs rdzogs dkyil 'khor phyir //
NG0200:1296: kun la rin chen dur khrod brgyan //
NG0200:1297: spel te mkhas pas bri bar bya //
NG0200:1298: mu khyud pad 'khor brag chen dang *//
NG0200:1299: rdo rje me ri 'khor yug bskor //
NG0200:1300: phyi gru nang khyud dur khrod brgyan //
NG0200:1301: mtshams bzhir dpag bsam bum pa br-i //
NG0200:1302: bsre bsnan bya zhing chas gos gsol //
NG0200:1303: gral bcas sman bsdu brda' sgo dbye //
NG0200:1304: brda' yi phyag btsal rtags mchog gdab //
NG0200:1305: dam bca' bshags pa byin chen dbab //
NG0200:1306: dkyil 'khor lha dang rgyan dgod de //
NG0200:1307: gling dgur b+han d+ha dgu'am ni //
NG0200:1308: bum gcig me gcig khram gcig dang *//
NG0200:1309: ta zhal phur gcig snying gcig dang */
NG0200:1310: sku gcig sku rten drag sngags dgod //
NG0200:1311: yang na mtshan ldan gcig nang du //
NG0200:1312: che mchog sku bri kha khyer la //
NG0200:1313: dpal chen dgu yi snying po bri //
NG0200:1314: sku dang gsung gi rten yin pas /
NG0200:1315: dmigs pa'i rten du dbus su dgod //
NG0200:1316: thugs rten rdo rje rtse lnga dgod //
NG0200:1317: yon tan rten du a mr-i ta //
NG0200:1318: phrin las bsgrub phyir lcags phur dgu / sras kyi sngags phur bzhi bzhis bskor //
NG0200:1319: sgo bzhi phur pa bzhi yang dgod //
NG0200:1320: gdab phur brgya dang rtsa brgyad kyis //
NG0200:1321: mtha' skor yongs rdzogs 'khor du bskyed //
NG0200:1322: sgo 'byed mar me dgu yang dgod //
NG0200:1324: yang phyogs bzhi mtshams brgyad du //
NG0200:1325: gri bzhi mda' bzhi me long bzhi //
NG0200:1326: phur bzhi tshon skud dra bas spras //
NG0200:1327: bla bre gdugs dang dar dbyangs 'phan //
NG0200:1328: dpal chen gtor chen dgu yang dgram //
NG0200:1329: sman rag d+ha ka'i mchod gtor sogs //
NG0200:1330: phyi nang mchod pas bklubs la dgang *//
NG0200:1331: de nas dngos gzhi bsnyen bsgrub bshad //
NG0200:1332: dang po phyi nang gsang mtshams bcad //
NG0200:1333: om badzra kro d+ha swa b+ha wa sa ma ya ru lu ru lu hum phat /
NG0200:1334: hum hum bi shwa badzra tsakra dz+wa la ma d+ha la /
NG0200:1337: de nas brda' sgo dbye bar bya /
NG0200:1339: de nas brda li phyag kyang btsal /
NG0200:1340: hum he ru ka a ti pu ho /
NG0200:1342: de nas dam bca' yongs su gzung *//
NG0200:1343: hum badzra sa ma ya hum /
NG0200:1344: de nas byin chen dbab par bya /
NG0200:1345: om shri badzra kro d+ha de ba dush+tan d+ha ki
NG0200:1346: ni sa ma ya ru lu ru lu hum b+h+yo
NG0200:1347: hum / a be sha ya a a /
NG0200:1348: de nas mchod pa byin brlabs 'bul //
NG0200:1356: badzra sarba pu dza me g+ha hum //
NG0200:1359: ma ha ba lim ta te dzo ba li te /
NG0200:1361: gu h+ya sa ma ya swa ha /
NG0200:1363: sarba pany+tsa a mr-i ta hum hri tha /
NG0200:1365: ma ha rak+ta sa man+ta man+dal hum phat /
NG0200:1366: om sarba ta tha ga ta ma ha pu dza /
NG0200:1367: ma ha pany+tsa ma ha ba lim ta /
NG0200:1371: de nas nyams chag gnong 'gyod bshags //
NG0200:1374: na ra ka / bre ta ka / tir ya ka / ma nu sha /
NG0200:1378: dag sha ka / bud+d+he shud+d+he swa ha /
NG0200:1379: sbyang gzhi sbyong byed thabs chen po //
NG0200:1380: khyad par bskyed rdzogs 'di ltar bsgom //
NG0200:1381: hum spros med yang dag de bzhin nyid //
NG0200:1382: mnyam yangs phyogs bral kun tu bdal //
NG0200:1383: ma nor ma bcos chos kyi sku //
NG0200:1384: rang bzhin lhun grub ngang gis gsal //
NG0200:1385: om ma ha shu n+ya ta dz+nya na badzra swa b+ha wa at+ma ko\u0f85ham /
NG0200:1386: de bzhin kun khyab kun tu snang *//
NG0200:1389: ma rtogs sems can snying re rje //
NG0200:1390: om d+harma d+ha tu swa b+ha wa bi shud+d+ha+e man+dal hum /
NG0200:1391: hum chos rnams rang byung rten 'brel te //
NG0200:1392: rgyu las ma byung gang yang med //
NG0200:1393: hum ni thams cad skyed pa'i rgyu //
NG0200:1394: dgos tshig rkang 'di med pa'ang 'dug 'dod 'byung ba'i yi ge bsgom //
NG0200:1395: rang rig don gyi snying po hum /
NG0200:1398: bskal pa gsum gyi 'jig rten stongs //
NG0200:1399: ye nas dag pa'i ngang nyid las //
NG0200:1400: snod bcud sbyang phyir 'byung rim brtseg / e yam ra sum kemram b+h+ram /
NG0200:1401: e las nam mkha' mtha' dbus med //
NG0200:1402: yam las rlung gi dkyil 'khor te //
NG0200:1404: sum las zhing chen sa gzhi brdal //
NG0200:1405: kem las rus pa'i ri rab steng *//
NG0200:1406: ram las bskal pa'i me dpung 'bar /
NG0200:1407: b+h+rum las ye shes gzhal yas khang */
NG0200:1411: b+han+da gnya' na e tsakra man+da la hum b+h+rum /
NG0200:1412: zla gam ye shes 'char sgo'i dbus //
NG0200:1413: chos sku 'gyur med e ru gsal //
NG0200:1414: b+han+da skam rlon pho brang brtseg / rin chen mdzes pa'i gling dgu la //
NG0200:1415: 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi mu khyud bcas //
NG0200:1416: gru chad bar khyams sgo khyud rdzogs //
