NG0200:2244: om b+ho d+hi tsit+ta ka ma la sid+d+hi hum ma ha su kha ho //
NG0200:2246: de nas bu la yum gtad de //
NG0200:2247: hum shes rab mtshan ldan bkra shis yum //
NG0200:2248: bden pa dbyer med bde chen bskyed //
NG0200:2249: 'khor lo'i gnas bzhir dbab bzung la //
NG0200:2250: brten nas chos nyid don rtogs byos //
NG0200:2251: om sarba ta tha ga ta gu h+ya pradz+nya sha ra swa b+ha wa at+ma ko\u0f85ham /
NG0200:2252: a ho su kha b+hany+dza mok+sha hoh /
NG0200:2253: de nas ras kyi yol ba'i phyir //
NG0200:2254: slob bu yab yum lhar gsal gdab //
NG0200:2255: rtsa rlung thig le'i gnad bstan la //
NG0200:2256: mkha' gsang byin brlab dbab gzung bzlog / dgram dang rgyas gdab 'khrul 'khor gyis //
NG0200:2257: bde mchog lhan skyes rtogs goms sbyang *//
NG0200:2258: sems kyi dri ma des dag pas //
NG0200:2259: bde chen lam bsgom rjes gnang sbyin //
NG0200:2260: de ltar yab yum sbyor ba'i tshe //
NG0200:2261: yul gsum gsal bar gyur ma gyur //
NG0200:2262: gsang ba'i dgra gsum sod ma sod //
NG0200:2263: 'jigs pa'i bdud bzhi chom ma choms //
NG0200:2264: 'gro drug g.yang sa chod ma chod //
NG0200:2265: tshad dang ldan nam bla mas brtag / ldan na
NG0200:2266: nyon mongs ma spangs dag / rang byung ye shes
NG0200:2267: rang shar te // sa rnams non te phyir mi ldog / go 'phang dbang gis bgrod par byed //
NG0200:2268: de nas rig pa'i dbang bskur te //
NG0200:2269: lag tu rdo rje dril bu gtad //
NG0200:2270: me long shel bcas brda' ru 'phyar //
NG0200:2271: tshig gis mtshon pa'i don ngo sprad //
NG0200:2272: hum sems nyid gsal la 'dzin rtog med //
NG0200:2273: ka dag lhun grub ye shes sku //
NG0200:2274: gnyis med 'dzin bral thugs rje'i gsung *//
NG0200:2275: rang rig yang dag rdo rje'i thugs //
NG0200:2278: de ltar gsang dbang yongs rdzogs nas //
NG0200:2279: yang gsang lta ba spyi 'byams dbang *//
NG0200:2280: yongs rdzogs rgyal thabs 'di nyid de //
NG0200:2281: shes rab mig ldan gcig la bskur //
NG0200:2282: slob dpon mnyam gzhag phyag rgya'i mthil //
NG0200:2283: a dkar gsal 'tsher gcig la gzhag / dgongs pa
NG0200:2284: chos nyid ngang la gzhag / slob bus nor bu
NG0200:2285: rin chen thogs // dpon dang slob bu yab yum kun //
NG0200:2286: kun bzang yab yum skur gsal gdab //
NG0200:2287: hum thams cad lhun grub kun tu bzang po dngos //
NG0200:2288: rang bzhin brjod med kun tu bzang mo'i ngang *//
NG0200:2289: gnyis med thabs kyi rgyal pos yongs la khyab //
NG0200:2290: dbyer med chos kyi dbyings su dbang bskur bas //
NG0200:2291: kun tu bzang po rang byung bcom ldan 'das //
NG0200:2292: chos kyi dbyings la gcig tu bzhugs pa yi //
NG0200:2293: rang rig byang chub sems kyi lha yin te //
NG0200:2294: don dam sems kyi lha la bdag phyag 'tshal //
NG0200:2295: phyag g.yas ar bcas slob bu'i spyi gtsug gzhag /
NG0200:2296: hum kun tu bzang po dri ma med pa yi
NG0200:2297: // yongs la dbang bsgyur ye shes rgyal por shar //
NG0200:2298: rang sems rnam dag lta ba'i rgyal por shar //
NG0200:2299: byang chub snying po bde ba chen por shar //
NG0200:2300: thams cad ma lus lhun grub chos kyi sku /
NG0200:2301: chos rnams thams cad rang gi sems su 'dus //
NG0200:2302: sems kyi bdag nyid ci yang ma yin pas //
NG0200:2303: thig le spros pa med pa'i rang bzhin nyid //
NG0200:2304: mnyam pa'i rgyal po kun la dbang bsgyur te //
NG0200:2305: chos nyid rig pa'i rgyal po rdzogs pa che //
NG0200:2306: ma 'dres cir yang ston pa theg pa'i mchog / 'di dag ma lus myur du rdzogs bya'i phyir //
NG0200:2307: spyi blugs lta ba'i dbang mchog 'di bskur bas //
NG0200:2308: yongs kyi dbang rdzogs stobs kyi rgyal por 'gyur //
NG0200:2309: om sarba ta tha ga ta pa la pa tra /
NG0200:2310: g+hu h+ya ra dza ta na sha sarba at+ma ko\u0f85ham /
NG0200:2311: de nas lta ba'i dbang bskur te /
NG0200:2312: slob ma'i mig mdun mkha' la gtad //
NG0200:2313: hum ltos shig ltos shig rigs kyi bu //
NG0200:2314: mdun gyi nam mkha' 'di la ltos //
NG0200:2315: gsal la dwangs pa mtha' dang bral //
NG0200:2317: lta ba phyogs lhung bral ba yin //
NG0200:2318: 'di nyid don la gnas par gyis //
NG0200:2319: dus gsum sangs rgyas dgongs pa yin //
NG0200:2321: de nas bsgom pa'i dbang bskur te /
NG0200:2322: hum ltos shig ltos shig rigs kyi bu //
NG0200:2323: rang gi sems la nang du ltos //
NG0200:2324: gsal la mi rtog ma yengs pa //
NG0200:2325: mar me rlung gis ma bskyod 'dra //
NG0200:2326: bsgom pa rang gsal 'dzin med yin //
NG0200:2327: 'di yi don la rtag tu sgoms //
NG0200:2328: dus gsum sangs rgyas bsgom nyams yin //
NG0200:2330: de nas 'bras bu'i dbang bskur te //
NG0200:2331: hum ltos shig ltos shig skal ldan khyod //
NG0200:2332: chos sku 'gyur med don la ltos //
NG0200:2333: smra bsam brjod pa'i mtha' las 'das //
NG0200:2335: gang yang ma grub stong pa'i ngang *//
NG0200:2336: mi skye mi 'gag chos kyi sku //
NG0200:2339: 'di yi don la gnas par gyis //
NG0200:2340: dus gsum sangs rgyas 'di la gnas //
NG0200:2342: de nas spyod pa'i dbang bskur te //
NG0200:2343: hum nyon cig skal ldan rigs kyi bu //
NG0200:2344: rang byung ye shes rol pa la //
NG0200:2345: ma 'gags thabs kyi rgyal po yis //
NG0200:2346: gang snang sangs rgyas mdzad spyod la //
NG0200:2347: ci bder spyod pa rang sar grol //
NG0200:2348: spyod pa spyi 'byams yangs dog med //
NG0200:2349: dus gsum sangs rgyas dgongs spyod yin //
NG0200:2351: de ltar lta bsgom spyod 'bras bzhi //
NG0200:2352: sus thob don la rab gnas na //
NG0200:2354: dbang rnams de las rab tu 'phros //
NG0200:2355: de phyir dbang gi rgyal po yin //
NG0200:2356: hum bskyed dang rdzogs dang rdzogs pa che //
NG0200:2358: ting 'dzin gsum dang dbang chen gsum //
NG0200:2359: cho ga gsum dang lhar gsal gdab //
NG0200:2360: byin brlab dbang bskur ye shes bstim //
NG0200:2361: phyi nang gsang ba phyag rgyas mchod //
NG0200:2362: bstod bskul 'dzab bsnyen dbul la sogs //
NG0200:2363: bskyed rim grol ba'i lam yin te //
NG0200:2364: thams cad sems kyi cho 'phrul yin //
NG0200:2365: rang sems rtsal sbyong chen po'o //
NG0200:2366: hum lha rnams gnas su rdzogs rim ni //
NG0200:2367: yid ni yab la chos ni yum //
NG0200:2368: phung po yab la 'byung ba yum //
NG0200:2369: rnam shes yab la yul lnga yum //
NG0200:2370: dbang po yab la dus bzhi yum //
NG0200:2371: nyon mongs drug ni sprul pa'i sku //
NG0200:2372: lus chos yab la mu bzhi yum //
NG0200:2373: thabs ni yab la shes rab yum //
NG0200:2374: rang bzhin de ltar shes pas na //
NG0200:2375: ma bsrungs ma bsgrubs rang lhar gnas //
NG0200:2376: rang byung gnas 'gyur rdzogs rim yin //
NG0200:2377: rang byung lhun rdzogs rdzogs chen ni //
NG0200:2378: sangs rgyas thabs mkhas thugs rje yis //
NG0200:2379: theg sgo bsam mi khyab gsungs kyang *//
NG0200:2380: thams cad blo yi 'bring thabs yin //
NG0200:2381: chos rnams thams cad sems su rdzogs //
NG0200:2382: chos kun bden pa dbyer med pas //
NG0200:2383: thams cad yin la gang yang min //
NG0200:2384: sangs rgyas mthar thug chos kyi sku //
NG0200:2385: kun la rdzogs te ngo ma shes //
NG0200:2386: hoh'khor ba dang ni mya ngan 'das //
NG0200:2388: yang dag don la dbye ba med //
NG0200:2389: gnyis ka rang gi sems la rdzogs //
NG0200:2390: hohchos su 'dzin pa thams cad ni //
NG0200:2391: spros pa blo yi chos yin phyir //
NG0200:2392: sku gsum rang yang grangs su zad //
NG0200:2393: 'dus byas chos kyis sangs mi rgya //
NG0200:2394: hohsangs rgyas chos su 'dzin pa ni //
NG0200:2395: mthar thug 'khrul blo chen po yin //
NG0200:2396: sangs ni chos min gcig gis rgya //
NG0200:2397: blo las 'das pa rdzogs chen yin //
NG0200:2398: hohrgyas bsdus rim par rang lus bzhin //
NG0200:2399: rim pa dbang gis bgrod par bya //
NG0200:2400: sa ma ya ni shel gong ltar //
NG0200:2401: gzhi ni dam tshig gtsang mas bzung *//
NG0200:2402: ting 'dzin lus dang grib ma ltar //
NG0200:2403: nyams su ting nge 'dzin gyis long *//
NG0200:2404: man ngag gar chang 'thung ba ltar //
NG0200:2405: don ni man ngag zab mos bsgrub //
NG0200:2406: lta ba nam mkha'i mdung skor @#//
NG0200:2408: thag dang 'phang ni lta bas bcad //
NG0200:2409: spyod pa mi sha rlon pa bzhin //
NG0200:2410: la ni spyod pas dor bar bya //
NG0200:2411: zung du 'brel la gol sa med //
NG0200:2412: tshig tu rtog la ma brten par //
NG0200:2413: sku gsum don po gcig tu dril //
NG0200:2414: mtha' drug rgyud la rdzogs par gyis //
NG0200:2415: mthar thug don dam nang nas 'char //
NG0200:2416: nam mkha' la ni nam mkha' bzhin //
NG0200:2417: thams cad stong pa'i ngang la gnas //
NG0200:2418: hohde ltar dbang rnams yongs rdzogs par //
NG0200:2419: bskur ba'i yon tan bsam mi khyab //
NG0200:2420: gsang sngags dngos grub dbang las 'byung *//
NG0200:2421: thob rtags mkha' 'gros lung bstan cing *//
NG0200:2422: ltas su yid bzhin gtsug na 'chang *//
NG0200:2423: mgo la nyi shar dmag dpon byed //
NG0200:2424: mgo dang ro stod yang la bde //
NG0200:2425: bum bcud 'thung dang zas bcud zos //
NG0200:2426: rang rig rtsal la dbang bsgyur nus //
NG0200:2427: dbang ma thob pa'i nyes pa ni //
NG0200:2428: shes rab gsum rlom las bsog kyang *//
NG0200:2429: 'bras bu med cing rlag par byed //
NG0200:2430: dbang yon ma phul shin tu nyams //
NG0200:2431: de nas dbang yon dbul ba ni //
NG0200:2432: byin rlobs dbang gi bla ma la //
NG0200:2433: rgyal srid yul 'khor rang gi lus //
NG0200:2434: bu dang chung ma nor dbyig dbul //
NG0200:2436: dpal gsang ba 'dus pa rgyud kyi rgyal po las /
NG0200:2437: gsang ba yongs rdzogs kyi dbang bskur ba'i le'u ste
NG0200:2438: bcu gcig pa'o // // de nas yang 'dus pa'i
NG0200:2440: ston pa kun tu bzang po dpal che mchog he ru ka la gsol pa /
NG0200:2442: dam tshig chen po kun tu bzang *//
NG0200:2443: rdo rje 'chang kun yongs kyi rje /
NG0200:2444: rgyud don dam tshig chos kyi srog / bdag cag
NG0200:2445: 'khor la bka' stsol cig / de skad gsol bar
NG0200:2446: don dgongs nas // ston pa nyid kyis bka' stsal pa //
NG0200:2448: rgyud don dam tshig bsrung bya ba /
NG0200:2449: rtsa ba sku gsung thugs dang ni //
NG0200:2450: yan lag nyi shu rtsa lnga las //
NG0200:2451: spros na bsam gyis mi khyab kyang *//
NG0200:2452: rtsa ba yan lag nyams mi bya //
NG0200:2453: yang na mnyam rdzogs chen por gnas //
NG0200:2454: sku yi dam tshig rdo rje ste //
NG0200:2455: slob dpon mched dang lcam dral la //
NG0200:2456: brdeg btsog skur ba nam yang min //
NG0200:2457: ngan sems 'phya sems gcig mi bya //
NG0200:2458: gsung gi dam tshig dbang thob nas //
NG0200:2459: yi dam dkyil 'khor lha tshogs kyi //
NG0200:2460: sngags dang phyag rgya rgyun mi gcad //
NG0200:2461: bla med theg mchog mi spang ngo *//
NG0200:2462: thugs kyi dam tshig gsang ba bcu //
NG0200:2463: gnas dang dus grogs thams cad gsang *//
NG0200:2464: sgrub rdzas lag cha thams cad gsang *//
NG0200:2466: sman dang gtor ma mchod rdzas gsang *//
NG0200:2467: de ma gsang na dngos grub nyams //
NG0200:2468: spyi 'dzab rtsa ba'i snying po gsang *//
NG0200:2469: ma gsang mthu dang byin brlabs nyams //
NG0200:2470: sngags pa sngags dang phyag rgya gsang *//
NG0200:2471: de ma gsang na smyon par 'gyur //
NG0200:2472: sbyor dang sgrol ba'i lag len gsang *//
NG0200:2475: phrin las mdzad spyod kun kyang gsang *//
NG0200:2476: de ma gsang na ras bar yang chod 'gyur //
NG0200:2477: rgyud dang sgrub thabs man ngag gsang *//
NG0200:2479: mdor na gsang ba 'os rigs gsang *//
NG0200:2480: de ma gsang na lkugs par 'gyur //
NG0200:2481: ched du gnyer gtad man ngag gsang *//
NG0200:2482: ma gsang nyams pa chen por 'gyur //
NG0200:2483: sku gsung thugs kyi dam tshig ni //
NG0200:2484: nyams na bskal pa gcig gnyis gsum //
NG0200:2485: rdo rje dmyal bar gdon mi za //
NG0200:2486: shes bya lnga dang spyad bya lnga //
NG0200:2487: mi spang lnga dang bsgrub bya lnga //
NG0200:2488: dang len lnga ni yan lag ste /
NG0200:2489: nyams na mnar med dmyal bar 'gro //
NG0200:2490: gzhan yang khyad par dam tshig dang *//
NG0200:2491: bla ma bkur zhing gsung mi bcag / thun bzhi'i rnal 'byor yengs mi bya //
NG0200:2492: lha dang sngags la the tshom spangs //
NG0200:2493: mched lcam kun la gdung sems bskyed //
NG0200:2494: sems can kun la snying rjes bskyang *//
NG0200:2495: nga rgyal rlom sems zhe sdang dang *//
NG0200:2496: 'dod chags phrag dog khar mi btang *//
NG0200:2497: gsang sngags lta spyod zung du sbrel //
NG0200:2498: bskyed rdzogs bsnyen bsgrub mtha' ru dbyung *//
NG0200:2499: le lo gnyid dang chang dbang spang *//
NG0200:2500: yang dag don gyi dam tshig tu //
NG0200:2502: gdod nas rang byung chos sku'i ngang *//
NG0200:2503: de nyid ye nas bsrung nyams ni //
NG0200:2504: mi bsrung blo yis dor du med //
NG0200:2505: nyams skyon thob bya'i 'bras bu med //
NG0200:2507: skye med gnyen pos mi shigs dam //
NG0200:2508: mu stegs bdag tu 'dzin pa tshig / snga rabs 'das pa'i sangs rgyas kyang *//
NG0200:2509: dam tshig dag la brten te rgyas //
NG0200:2510: da ltar bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas kyang *//
NG0200:2511: dam tshig 'di la rab tu gnas //
NG0200:2512: slad kyis 'byon pa'i sangs rgyas kyang *//
NG0200:2513: dam tshig dag la brten nas rgya //
NG0200:2515: dpal gsang ba 'dus pa rgyud kyi rgyal po las /
NG0200:2516: dam tshig dag la brten pa'i le'u ste bcu gnyis pa'o ///
NG0200:2517: / de nas yang 'dus pa'i 'khor rnams kyis mgrin
NG0200:2518: gcig tu ston pa kun tu bzang po dpal che
NG0200:2519: mchog he ru ka la gsol pa /
NG0200:2521: sprul pa'i sku mchog kun tu bzang *//
NG0200:2522: skye med chos te sna tshogs ston //
NG0200:2523: rgyud don mtha' rgyas yid bzhin gter //
NG0200:2524: bdag cag rnams la bka' stsol cig / de skad gsol pa'i don dgongs te //
NG0200:2525: ston pa nyid kyis bka' stsal pa //
NG0200:2526: rgyud don mtha' rgyas cha dang rkyen //
NG0200:2527: man ngag la sogs bsam yas kyang *//
NG0200:2528: dgos pa mdo tsam bshad par bya //
NG0200:2529: ji ltar 'dod pa'i don rjod cig / de skad rjes su gnang ba dang *//
NG0200:2530: gsang ba'i bdag po rdo rje chos //
NG0200:2531: dga' zhing mgu nas thal mo sbyar //
NG0200:2532: kye ho dpal chen yid bzhin mdzod //
NG0200:2533: bde gshegs zhi khro yongs rdzogs pa'i //
NG0200:2534: gsang ba 'dus pa'i rgyud mchog gi / nyams len
NG0200:2535: mdor bsdus bka' stsol cig / de skad gsol pa'i
NG0200:2537: bde gshegs yongs rdzogs gsang rgyud kyi //
NG0200:2538: mdor bsdus nyams len sgrub lugs gsum //
NG0200:2539: skye dang rdzogs dang rdzogs chen te //
NG0200:2540: gcig la gcig brten gcig gi ngang *//
NG0200:2541: phyi dang nang dang gsang ba'i tshul //
NG0200:2542: phyi ni rdul tshon dkyil 'khor la //
NG0200:2543: brten nas skyed pa'i rnal 'byor ni //
NG0200:2544: gong du bstan pa'i sgrub chen yin //
NG0200:2545: de yang gang zag blo rigs kyis //
NG0200:2546: rab tu spros la mi dga' bas //
NG0200:2547: sku gsung thugs kyi sgrub pa'am //
NG0200:2548: yang na zhi khro dgos sgrub bam //
NG0200:2549: che mchog yab yum gnyis su dril //
NG0200:2550: thugs sgrub hum du bsgrub kyang rung *//
NG0200:2551: rgyud 'di sor gzhag kho na ltar //
NG0200:2552: bde gshegs rtsa ba yongs rdzogs pas //
NG0200:2553: rigs lnga zhi khro bka' brgyad gtso //
NG0200:2554: rtsa ba'i lha tshogs go gcig skyed //
NG0200:2555: nyi ma dang ni zer bzhin du //
NG0200:2556: 'khor rnams rang bzhin lhan skyes rung *//
NG0200:2557: mdor na sku mdog phyag mtshan sogs //
NG0200:2558: zhal phyag mang nyung bsam yas kyang *//
NG0200:2559: ye shes lha la rang rgyud par //
NG0200:2560: rtsis gdab khrigs su gcad pa med //
NG0200:2561: gdul bya'i blo dang gang mthun par //
NG0200:2562: chos sku'i rang rtsal cir yang snang *//
NG0200:2563: thams cad sems kyi cho 'phrul yin //
NG0200:2565: rgyas bsdus gang ltar bsgom yang rung *//
NG0200:2566: nyams len bde la don mi 'gyur //
NG0200:2567: de phyir bde chen g.yung drung lha //
NG0200:2569: sems 'dzin sems kyi rtsal sbyangs pas //
NG0200:2570: de phyir sgrub chen bskyed pa yin //
NG0200:2571: nang ni lus kyi dkyil 'khor 'di nyid la //
NG0200:2572: brten nas rdzogs pa'i rnal 'byor bstan pa ni /
NG0200:2573: sngon 'gro'i las rnams kyang gsum sngon du song byas nas //
NG0200:2574: ma bskyed rdzogs pa'i ldan tshul lha bsgom pa //
NG0200:2575: ye nas kun gzhi stong gsal de bzhin nyid //
NG0200:2576: de nyid kun khyab kun snang snying rje'i ngang *//
NG0200:2577: 'gag med rol ba hum ni kun gyi rgyu //
NG0200:2578: ma bskyed rdzogs pa'i ting 'dzin rnam gsum bsgom //
NG0200:2579: de bzhin 'byung ba rim pa lnga brtseg kyang *//
NG0200:2580: ma bskyed rang la rdzogs tshul 'di ltar bsgom //
NG0200:2581: sems nyid nam mkha' stong gsal e yi ngang *//
NG0200:2582: 'gyu byed 'thor rlung skyod byed stobs ldan yam //
NG0200:2583: sdud byed khrag gyi rgya mtsho chu yin ra //
NG0200:2584: gzugs ni rab brtan sha ni sa yin sum //
NG0200:2585: smin byed drod kyi rang bzhin me yin ram //
NG0200:2586: sgal tshigs rus pa'i ri rab brtsegs pas kem //
NG0200:2587: khog pa gzhal yas khang gi rang bzhin b+h+rum /
NG0200:2588: yab yum byang sems dkar dang dmar mthing gis //
NG0200:2589: srog rtsa dbu ma drang po tshangs pa'i thig /
NG0200:2590: 'khor lo bzhi yi tshangs thig cha bzhir bgo /
NG0200:2591: rtse chung gnyis rtse tshangs pa'i rtsa la zug /
NG0200:2592: de smad rtse chen long rtsa gnyis la zug /
NG0200:2593: lag gnyis blta rtsa bla rtsa rnam pa gnyis //
NG0200:2594: phan tshul bsnol nas 'brel pa rtsa gnyis te //
NG0200:2595: de bzhin srog pa'i rtsa la rab tu gyes //
NG0200:2596: pho brang ling tshe dgu yi tshul du tshang *//
NG0200:2597: ling tshe re la rtsa yi 'dab bzhi @#//
NG0200:2599: phyogs bzhir gyes pas 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi'i tshul //
NG0200:2600: rtsa yi rgyal po srog pa'i rtsa de las //
NG0200:2601: rtsa chen bzhi gyes rtsa chen cha gcig ni //
NG0200:2602: a wa la thug dbang po 'char byed rtsa //
NG0200:2603: rtsa bran lnga brgya'i 'khor dang 'du 'phro byed //
NG0200:2604: rtsa chen gcig dang gnyis 'brel dbang po rgyu //
NG0200:2605: rtsa bran lnga brgya'i 'khor dang 'du 'phro byed //
NG0200:2606: rtsa chen gcig dang de ltar 'brel byed pa'i //
NG0200:2607: 'khor lo sgyur byed rgyu yang rtsa ste lnga brgyar ldan //
NG0200:2608: rtsa chen gcig dang gsang 'brel 'byung byed rtsa //
NG0200:2609: rtsa bran lnga brgya'i 'khor dang 'phro 'du byed //
NG0200:2610: de yang klad pa'i a wa d+hu ti las //
NG0200:2611: mtshon rtsa dgu bcu phyi nang rten 'brel gyis //
NG0200:2612: dbang po rgyu byed rtsa la de bzhin pas //
NG0200:2613: 'khor lo sgyur yang rgyu byed rtsa la de bzhin pas //
NG0200:2614: 'byung ba skyed byed rtsa la de bzhin no //
NG0200:2615: brgya dang nyi shu lpags pa'i mtshon rtsa yin //
NG0200:2616: brgya dang nyi shu rus pa'i mtshon rtsa yin //
NG0200:2617: brgyad dang nyi shu gdags sribs mtshon pa'i rtsa //
NG0200:2618: rtsa ba'i rtsa bzhi srog pa'i rtsa dang lnga //
NG0200:2619: de ltar bdun brgya nyi shu rtsa lnga po //
NG0200:2620: bde gshegs bdun brgya nyer lnga'i pho brang yin //
NG0200:2621: ma bskyed rang rtsal yongs su rdzogs pa ste //
NG0200:2622: de bzhin b+han+d+ha'i gzhal yas rang gi mgo / snying nang zla gam ye shes dgu 'char bas //
NG0200:2623: zla gam sgo dgu dngos grub yid bzhin gter //
NG0200:2624: tsit+ta'i pho long ba su'i dra phyed dang *//
NG0200:2625: zhing lpags bla bre rak+ta'i rgya mtsho dang *//
NG0200:2626: sha chen keng rus dri chen dri chu dang *//
NG0200:2627: nang gi dur khrod gnas brgyad rang la tshang *//
NG0200:2628: nyi zla'i skar khung rang gi mig gnyis la //
NG0200:2629: kha sna gsang bshad dkyil 'khor sgo bzhi yin //
NG0200:2630: de ltar gzhal yas ye nas rang la rdzogs //
NG0200:2631: lha rnams rang la yongs rdzogs 'di ltar bsgom //
NG0200:2632: srog rtsa lus kyi dkyil 'khor dbus yin te //
NG0200:2633: kun gzhi sems kyi rang bzhin de la brten //
NG0200:2634: de phyir che chog yab yum rang rdzogs bsgom //
NG0200:2635: srog rtsa'i shar phyogs snying yin rig pa shar //
NG0200:2636: thugs mchog badzra he ru yab yum bsgom //
NG0200:2637: srog rtsa'i lho mgo dbang po yon tan rgyas //
NG0200:2638: sku mchog gshin rje gshed po yab yum bsgom //
NG0200:2639: srog rtsa'i nub mgrin rtsa 'dus ro mchog nub //
NG0200:2640: gsung mchog pad+ma dbang chen yab yum bsgom //
NG0200:2641: srog rtsa'i byang ste srid pa lte nas chags //
NG0200:2642: phrin las rdo rje gzhon nu yab yum bskyed //
NG0200:2643: srog rtsa'i shar lho gsang gnas bde ba 'bar //
NG0200:2644: bla med he ru ka chen yab yum bsgom //
NG0200:2645: srog rtsa'i lho nub spyi bo dbang gi gnas //
NG0200:2646: rig 'dzin bla ma rdo rje thod rtsal bsgom //
NG0200:2647: srog rtsa'i nub byang rkang g.yas ngar gdong du //
NG0200:2648: rab 'jigs dregs pa kun 'dul yab yum bsgom //
NG0200:2649: srog rtsa'i byang shar rkang g.yon ngar gdong du //
NG0200:2650: bdud 'dul stobs ldan nag po yab yum bsgom //
NG0200:2651: phyi lpags khyams yin lus khyab rab tu gtums //
NG0200:2652: pags pa'i rtsa bran bka' sdod pho nyar bsgom //
NG0200:2654: gnyer sul rdo rje rwa ba ste //
NG0200:2655: ba spu rnams ni bskal pa'i me ri'o //
NG0200:2656: de ltar gsang ba yongs rdzogs lha rnams kyang *//
NG0200:2657: rang rgyud phyogs ris dngos por 'dzin med pas //
NG0200:2658: tshom bu gtso rkyang yab yum gang gsal rung *//
NG0200:2659: dbu dang phyag zhabs mang nyung dbyibs kha dog / ji ltar mos pa'i rjes 'breng rig rtsal yin //
NG0200:2660: de ltar ye rdzogs don shes rang gsal na //
NG0200:2661: spyan drangs bstim mchod bstod bshags bya ba rdzogs //
NG0200:2662: 'dzab kyang rlung gi sgra skad rang sgrar ldan //
NG0200:2663: hum ring hum thung khro rgyal kun 'dus sngags //
NG0200:2664: rang byung rdo rje'i glu yis bzlas pa'i tshe //
NG0200:2665: khro tshogs kun gyis dir dir sgrogs par bsam //
NG0200:2666: 'od zer mar 'phros sgo gsum sgrib pa sbyang *//
NG0200:2667: 'od zer gyen rdzogs rdzogs pa'i rim pa bsgom //
NG0200:2668: rtsol med rang rdzogs rtsal sbyangs pas //
NG0200:2669: de phyir rdzogs pa nang sgrub yin //
NG0200:2670: gsang ba sems kyi dkyil 'khor la //
NG0200:2671: brten nas rdzogs chen rnal 'byor ni //
NG0200:2672: gnyis te dkyil 'khor rang rig la //
NG0200:2673: rdzogs pa'i tshul dang nyams len no //
NG0200:2674: rang rig sems su lha rdzogs tshul //
NG0200:2675: snying po rang rig 'khrul mtshams chod //
NG0200:2676: nga bdag dgra bgegs ming med rdzogs //
NG0200:2677: rang sems rtsa bral rang rig pas //
NG0200:2678: bshags bya 'chags byed med par rdzogs //
NG0200:2679: spros bral byin gyis ye shes phebs //
NG0200:2680: byin rlabs rang byung chen por rdzogs //
NG0200:2681: rig pa ye shes 'char sgo phye //
NG0200:2682: brda' sgo dbyer med ngang du rdzogs //
NG0200:2683: chos min don dang rang rig mjal //
NG0200:2684: brda phyag btsal du med par rdzogs //
NG0200:2685: rang sems rdzas mchog 'dod dgur bsgyur //
NG0200:2686: mchod rdzas bsham du med par rdzogs //
NG0200:2687: skye 'gag gnyis med rang byung lha'i //
NG0200:2688: ting 'dzin dbye bsal med par rdzogs //
NG0200:2690: dbang chen yum lnga dbyer med rdzogs //
NG0200:2691: don gyi snying po tshad las 'das //
NG0200:2692: gzhal yas gsal 'grib med par rdzogs //
NG0200:2693: bde gsal mi rtog dbyer med pas //
NG0200:2694: nyi zla pad gdan mtshon med rdzogs //
NG0200:2695: kun gzhi ma bcos klong yangs su //
NG0200:2696: yid byed dran pa rnam par dag / ye shes sems dpa' chos skur rdzogs //
NG0200:2697: bdag med rang rig byang chub sems //
NG0200:2698: gti mug rnam dag chos kyi dbyings //
NG0200:2699: ye shes rang shar bde chen don //
NG0200:2700: che mchog he ru'i ngo bor rdzogs //
NG0200:2701: zhe sdang rang rgyud rang dag gis //
NG0200:2702: ye shes rang shar bde gshegs thugs //
NG0200:2703: badzra he ru'i ngo bor rdzogs //
NG0200:2704: nga rgyal rang dag mnyam nyid kyi //
NG0200:2705: ye shes rang shar bde gshegs sku //
NG0200:2706: gshin rje gshed po'i ngo bor rdzogs //
NG0200:2707: 'dod chags rang dag kun rtog gi / ye shes rang shar bde gshegs gsung *//
NG0200:2708: dbang chen rta mgrin ngo bor rdzogs //
NG0200:2709: phrag dog rang dag nan tan gyi //
NG0200:2710: ye shes rang shar bde gshegs phrin //
NG0200:2711: rdo rje gzhon nu'i ngo bor rdzogs //
NG0200:2712: bag chags mngon gyur byang chub @#//
NG0200:2714: chos kyi skur snang brjid pa'i stobs //
NG0200:2715: bla med he ru'i ngo bor rdzogs //
NG0200:2716: rnam rtog 'gyu byed yid dag pas //
NG0200:2717: longs spyod rdzogs sku 'jigs pa'i stobs //
NG0200:2718: dregs pa kun 'dul ngo bor rdzogs //
NG0200:2719: dug lnga phrag dog rnam dag pas //
NG0200:2720: sprul sku sna tshogs gyad kyi stobs //
NG0200:2721: stobs ldan nag po'i ngo bor rdzogs //
NG0200:2722: sgyu lus rdos bcas rnam dag pas //
NG0200:2723: rgyal ba rig 'dzin thogs med stobs //
NG0200:2724: rdo rje slob dpon ngo bor rdzogs //
NG0200:2725: 'jig rten 'dzin rtog rnam par dag / bstan pa bsrung mdzad mthun chen stobs //
NG0200:2726: dpal gyi bka' srung ngo bor rdzogs //
NG0200:2727: de ltar yongs rdzogs rgyal ba rnams //
NG0200:2728: cir yang snang thabs yab kyi tshul //
NG0200:2729: shes rab mon 'das yum gyi ngang *//
NG0200:2730: lha tshogs de dag thams cad kyang *//
NG0200:2731: ye shes mtshon phyir ming du btags //
NG0200:2732: don la rang byung ye shes sku //
NG0200:2733: ma bcos thig le nyag gcig yin //
NG0200:2734: ye nas rang dang lhan cig gnas //
NG0200:2735: spyan drang bzhugs gsol mi dgos rdzogs //
NG0200:2736: bzang ngan med mnyam gnyis med mchod //
NG0200:2737: phyag dang mchod pa mi dgos rdzogs //
NG0200:2738: rang rtsal thabs kyis 'gro don mdzad //
NG0200:2739: phrin las bstod bskul mi dgos rdzogs //
NG0200:2740: mtha' bral snying po brjod du med //
NG0200:2741: bsnyen sgrub 'dzab bzlas mi dgos rdzogs //
NG0200:2742: rang rig dri med 'od gsal lha //
NG0200:2743: chos sku lhun grub 'bras bu yin //
NG0200:2744: de ltar rdzogs pa'i don shes na //
NG0200:2745: gsang ba'i nyams len mthar thug pas //
NG0200:2746: rdzogs pa chen po'i sdom bzhi yin //
NG0200:2747: gza' gtad med pa'i lta ba yis //
NG0200:2748: yin pa med par rang ngo sprad //
NG0200:2749: dmigs gtad med pa'i sgom pa yis /
NG0200:2750: mi nang med par nyams su blangs //
NG0200:2751: blang dor med pa'i spyod pa yis //
NG0200:2752: yin min med par 'gag kyang bsdam //
NG0200:2753: spang thob med pa'i 'bras bu yis //
NG0200:2754: re dang dogs pa'i gol sa bcad //
NG0200:2755: lta ba'i ngo sprod don gsum ste //
NG0200:2756: chos rnams mnyam nyid ngo sprod cing *//
NG0200:2757: grub mtha'i phyogs 'dzin grol ba dang *//
NG0200:2758: phyogs ris med par la bzla'o //
NG0200:2759: mnyam nyid rang ngo sprad pa ni //
NG0200:2761: snang ba chos nyid ma yin par //
NG0200:2762: stong pa chos nyid yin pa'am //
NG0200:2763: chos can ma yin chos nyid gcig / logs nas 'byung bar 'dod pa'am //
NG0200:2764: yod min med min yin sems mam //
NG0200:2765: rang min gzhan min rtog pa'am //
NG0200:2766: rdzun min bden pa min zhe na //
NG0200:2767: de ltar tha dad ma yin te //
NG0200:2768: chos rnams rang byung ye shes nyid //
NG0200:2769: chos min gtad med nyid snang ba //
NG0200:2770: snang na rang snang stong rang stong *//
NG0200:2771: snang dang stong pa ye nas mnyam //
NG0200:2772: chos can nyid na chos nyid pas //
NG0200:2773: chos can chos nyid ye nas mnyam //
NG0200:2774: yod pa'i dus na rang bzhin med //
NG0200:2775: yod dang med pa ye nas mnyam //
NG0200:2776: rang mi snang bar gzhan mi snang *//
NG0200:2777: rang dang gzhan du ye nas mnyam //
NG0200:2778: rdzun pa nyid na don nyid bden //
NG0200:2782: ci phyir zhe na sems nyid kyi //
NG0200:2783: ngo bo phyogs lhung gang yang min //
NG0200:2784: de phyir chos min gtad med de //
NG0200:2785: dper na ga pur sman dug bzhin //
NG0200:2786: ye nas mnyam nyid rang ngo sprad //
NG0200:2787: grub mtha'i phyogs 'dzin grol ba yin //
NG0200:2788: chos rnams mnyam nyid mtha' grol la //
NG0200:2789: byis pas rang rgyud bzung ba 'khrul //
NG0200:2790: chad pas stong par bzung bas log / theg dman snang ba dgrar bltas gol //
NG0200:2791: byang sems gnyen pos sbyangs pas bsgribs //
NG0200:2793: sngags la phyi nang dag snang du //
NG0200:2794: bsgyur bas chos min gting ma rtogs //
NG0200:2795: mdor na phyogs 'dzin lta ba'i bdud //
NG0200:2796: gza' gtad med pa'i lta ba yis //
NG0200:2797: chos min rtogs pas phyogs 'dzin grol //
NG0200:2798: phyogs ris med pa'i la bzla ni //
NG0200:2799: chos can dngos po gang rung la //
NG0200:2800: byung tshul ming gzugs mtshan dpe dang *//
NG0200:2801: las dang kha dog dbyibs su bral //
NG0200:2802: bsam pas brtags na 'di yin med //
NG0200:2803: yod pa'i phyogs su ma lhung zhing *//
NG0200:2804: cir yang snang bas med pa yi //
NG0200:2805: phyogs su yang ni rgya ma chad //
NG0200:2806: gnyis ka'i ngos nas rang snang ba'i //
NG0200:2807: gnyis med phyogs su ma lhung bas //
NG0200:2808: mnyam nyid rgya chad ris med par //
NG0200:2809: yang dag don gyi la bzla'o //
NG0200:2810: bsgom pa'i nyams len la gsum ste //
NG0200:2811: bdag 'dzin ro dang dbral ba dang *//
NG0200:2812: bden rdzun 'khrul pa gzhig pa dang *//
NG0200:2813: yin min blo dang dbral ba'o //
NG0200:2814: bdag 'dzin ro dang dbral ba ni //
NG0200:2815: sgom byed mkhan po nga bdag ste //
NG0200:2816: bsgom bya sgom byed dmigs pas 'khor //
NG0200:2817: nga bdag nyid kyis nyid la brtag / ngo bo lus sems gang gis byas //
NG0200:2818: lus kyis byas na mgo yan lag / don lnga snod drug sha rus lpags //
NG0200:2819: gang gis byas te der mi snang *//
NG0200:2820: gal te sems kyis byas sems na //
NG0200:2821: ngo bo stong pas byed mkhan med //
NG0200:2822: rang bzhin gsal yang gzhi rtsa bral //
NG0200:2824: gang yang ma grub bdag ma rnyed //
NG0200:2825: de ma rnyed pas bsgom bya yi //
NG0200:2826: chos dang spang bya'i snang ba zhig / de phyir dmigs gtad kun dang bral //
NG0200:2827: bdag 'dzin ro med ngo sprod do //
NG0200:2828: bden rdzun 'khrul pa zhig pa ni //
NG0200:2829: phyi yi snang yul rang rgyud par //
NG0200:2830: bden cing grub pa med par nges //
NG0200:2831: bden na rigs drug ltar snang dang *//
NG0200:2832: mu stegs rtag chad theg dgu yi //
NG0200:2833: mthong snang tha dad ci la rigs //
NG0200:2834: de phyir chos min rang snang zhing *//
NG0200:2835: snang ba'i byed mkhan ma grub pas //
NG0200:2836: snang yul bden rdzun 'khrul snang zhig / gnyis 'dzin 'khrul pa gzhi rtsa bral //
NG0200:2837: yin min blo dang phral ba ni //
NG0200:2838: de ltar 'khrul gzhi rtsa bral bas //
NG0200:2839: bsgrub bya 'di yin bsgrub tu med //
NG0200:2840: spang bya 'di min spang du med //
NG0200:2841: thams cad yul med rig pa nyid //
NG0200:2842: phyogs med rang snang yul med grol //
NG0200:2843: yin min blo dang der bral mod //
NG0200:2846: chos byas gzung 'dzin gcad bya zhing *//
NG0200:2847: ma bcad lhun grub rdzogs pa dang *//
NG0200:2848: sgyu ma mnyam nyid 'gag bsdam mo //
NG0200:2849: ched byas gzung 'dzin bcad pa ni //
NG0200:2850: gza' gtad med pa'i lta ba yis //
NG0200:2851: yin pa med pa'i phyogs las grol //
NG0200:2852: dmigs gtad med pa'i bsgom pa yis //
NG0200:2853: min pa med par grogs su 'char //
NG0200:2854: blang dor med pa'i spyod pa yis //
NG0200:2855: yin min med pas ci yang spyad //
NG0200:2856: chos nyid klong las 'das pa med //
NG0200:2857: dge bcu pha rol phyin drug dang *//
NG0200:2858: chos spyod bcu sogs 'di blang bya //
NG0200:2859: mi dge bcu dang mtshams med lnga //
NG0200:2860: rnam smin sdig che 'di sbyang bya //
NG0200:2861: mtshan ma rang dag gzhi med pas //
NG0200:2862: blang dor gzung 'dzin ming med de //
NG0200:2863: yin min gnyis kyi chos las 'das //
NG0200:2864: ma spyad lhun grub rdzogs tshul ni //
NG0200:2865: de ltar lta sgom chos nyid kyi //
NG0200:2866: ngang las 'gro sa ma rnyed pas //
NG0200:2867: mi dge bcu dang sgrib gnyis sogs //
NG0200:2868: ma spangs chos min lhun gyis grub //
NG0200:2869: dge bcu chos spyod tshogs chen gnyis //
NG0200:2870: ma btsal chos min lhun gyis grub //
NG0200:2871: bsgrub bya sku dang ye shes sogs //
NG0200:2872: ma sgrubs lhun gyis rdzogs pa'o //
NG0200:2873: sgyu ma mnyam nyid 'gag bsdam ni //
NG0200:2875: sgyu ma'i dpe dgu ji bzhin du //
NG0200:2876: yod nas snang ba ma yin te //
NG0200:2877: yod pa nyid nas rang snang phyir //
NG0200:2878: skye ba med pas thams cad skye //
NG0200:2879: skyes tsam nyid nas skye med de //
NG0200:2880: snang ba'i dus na snang bar mnyam //
NG0200:2881: stong pa'i dus na stong par mnyam //
NG0200:2882: gnyis ga'i dus na gnyis su mnyam //
NG0200:2883: gnyis med gnyis su med par mnyam //
NG0200:2884: mnyam nyid phyogs las grol bas na //
NG0200:2885: sgyu ma lta bur 'gag bsdam mo //
NG0200:2886: 'bras bu'i la bzla la yang gsum //
NG0200:2888: spang thob mtshan med gtan tshigs dang *//
NG0200:2889: bsgrub med ye rdzogs la bzla'o //
NG0200:2891: gong bzhin bdag 'dzin ro bral bas //
NG0200:2892: rgyu ni sems can yul las 'das //
NG0200:2893: chos nyid ci yang ma yin pas //
NG0200:2895: mnyam nyid phyogs bral 'dzin med pas //
NG0200:2898: gnyis med kyi yang yul las 'das //
NG0200:2899: spang thob med pa'i gtan tshigs ni //
NG0200:2900: bsgom pa min pa med pas na //
NG0200:2901: gang snang thams cad grogs su shar //
NG0200:2902: de la spang bya'i yul med pas //
NG0200:2903: lta ba yin pa med pas na //
NG0200:2904: phyogs las grol te thob yul med //
NG0200:2905: de phyir spang thob mtshan ma med //
NG0200:2906: bsgrub med ye rdzogs la zlo ni //
NG0200:2907: lta ba yin pa med par rtogs //
NG0200:2908: mngon du gyur pas chos kyi sku //
NG0200:2909: sgom pa yin pa med pa ru //
NG0200:2910: rang sar grol bas longs spyod sku //
NG0200:2911: spyod pa min pa med pa ru //
NG0200:2912: 'gro don rdzogs pa sprul pa'i sku //
NG0200:2913: gnyis ka chos nyid de bzhin nyid //
NG0200:2916: phyogs bral kun rdzogs chen po ru //
NG0200:2917: la zlos chos zad bde chen sku //
NG0200:2918: de ltar klong gyur ma btsal bar //
NG0200:2919: ye nas lhun gyis yongs rdzogs pas //
NG0200:2920: re dogs gnas med la bzla'o //
NG0200:2921: de ltar nyams su len pa ni //
NG0200:2922: yongs rdzogs a ti'i dgongs pa ste //
NG0200:2923: rgyud mchog 'di yi khong snying yin //
NG0200:2925: dpal gsang ba 'dus pa rgyud kyi rgyal po las //
NG0200:2926: gsang ba nyams len yongs rdzogs mdor bsdus kyi le'u
NG0200:2927: ste bcu gsum pa'o // // de nas yang 'dus
NG0200:2929: ston pa kun tu bzang po dpal che mchog he ru ka la gsol pa /
NG0200:2931: srid pa'i rgyal po kun tu bzang *//
NG0200:2932: rtsa ba'i che mchog he ru ka / lus gnad rtsa yi man ngag gnad //
NG0200:2933: bdag cag rnams la bka' stsol cig / de skad gsol ba'i don dgongs nas //
NG0200:2934: ston pa nyid kyis bka' stsal pa //
NG0200:2935: spyir na rnal 'byor lus gnad rtsa //
NG0200:2936: stong phrag phyed dang bzhi brgyar 'dus //
NG0200:2937: de las bsdu na stong phrag gcig / bdun cu rtsa gnyis de bsdu na //
NG0200:2938: nyis khri chig stong drug brgya yod //
NG0200:2939: de yang bsdu na 'khor lo bzhi //
NG0200:2940: de bsdus la la ra sa na //
NG0200:2941: a wad+hu ti dang gsum mo //
NG0200:2942: rtsa rnams lus la gnas tshul ni //
NG0200:2943: dra ba g.yogs bzhin 'brel nas gnas //
NG0200:2944: rags pa 'khor lo bzhi yi rtsa //
NG0200:2945: spyi gtsug klad pa bde chen gyi //
NG0200:2947: gdugs rtsibs ltar gnas de dbus na //
NG0200:2948: yi ge ham mgo thur bsten gnas //
NG0200:2949: mgrin pa longs spyod 'khor lo ah //
NG0200:2950: rtsa 'dab bcu drug gnas lugs ni //
NG0200:2951: bum ske'i dra ba lta bur gnas //
NG0200:2952: snying ga chos kyi 'khor lo na //
NG0200:2954: de dbus yi ge hum du gnas //
NG0200:2955: lte ba sprul pa'i 'khor lo na //
NG0200:2956: rtsa 'dab drug cu rtsa gnyis ni //
NG0200:2957: gser khri lta bur gnas pa'i dbus //
NG0200:2958: rtsibs bzhi'i dbus na ma a yang gnas so //
NG0200:2959: phyi ni 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi'i tshul //
NG0200:2960: dbus na ye shes rtsa gnas pa //
NG0200:2961: de mdun gti mug g.yas zhe sdang *//
NG0200:2962: g.yon na nga rgyal phrag dog zur //
NG0200:2963: rgyab na 'dod chags rtsa gnas so //
NG0200:2964: dbus kyi rtsa mchog a d+hu ti //
NG0200:2965: g.yas kyi rtsa mchog la la na'o //
NG0200:2966: g.yon kyi rtsa mchog ra sa na'o //
NG0200:2967: d+hu ti rang la gsum yin te //
NG0200:2968: thabs kyi d+hu ti rgyungs pa ste //
NG0200:2969: de nas byang sems dkar po rgyu //
NG0200:2970: shes rab d+hu ti srog pa'i rtsa //
NG0200:2971: de nas byang sems dmar po rgyu //
NG0200:2972: gsang ba a wa d+hu ti'i rtsa //
NG0200:2973: rtsa gnyis bar na drang por gnas //
NG0200:2974: de ni dper na ba thag la //
NG0200:2975: nyi zer phog pa lta bur yod //
NG0200:2976: de nyid rtsa ba mtshan mar zug / rtse mo spyi gtsug 'khor lo'i dbus //
NG0200:2977: tshangs pa'i bu ga'i nang na gnas //
NG0200:2978: de nas sor gsum klad pa'i dbus //
NG0200:2979: bde ba chen po'i 'khor lo ste //
NG0200:2980: rtsa 'dab sum cu rtsa gnyis kyi //
NG0200:2981: dbus na de nyid gnas pa yin //
NG0200:2984: mgrin pa longs spyod 'khor lo yi //
NG0200:2985: rtsa 'dab bcu drug dbus na yang *//
NG0200:2986: de nyid zang thal gnas pa yin //
NG0200:2987: de nas an stong rus pa yi //
NG0200:2988: tshigs gnyis bar nas mdun du 'khyog / snying ga chos 'khor rtsa 'dab brgyad //
NG0200:2989: de nyid dbus na zang thal te //
NG0200:2991: drug cu rtsa gnyis dbus zang thal //
NG0200:2993: g.yas kyi la la na yi rtsa //
NG0200:2994: dbu ma'i g.yas 'grims yar phyung ste //
NG0200:2995: mig g.yas lcibs la slebs nas su //
NG0200:2996: sna sgo g.yas nas rlung rgyu ba'i //
NG0200:2997: las kyang de yis byed pa yin //
NG0200:2998: de rtsa ltag pa g.yas su 'khyog / an stong rus pa'i d+hu ti la //
NG0200:3000: spu ni nag gu'i mtshams su sleb //
NG0200:3001: g.yon phyogs ra sa na'i rtsa yang *//
NG0200:3002: yar 'gug mig g.yon lcibs su sleb //
NG0200:3003: sna sgo g.yon nas rlung rgyu ba'i //
NG0200:3004: las kyang de yis byed pa yin //
NG0200:3005: de rtsa ltag pa'i an stong nas //
NG0200:3006: d+hu ti dang gshibs spu nag gu'i //
NG0200:3007: dkyil du slebs nas gnas pa yin //
NG0200:3008: de ltar g.yas g.yon mar sna gnyis //
NG0200:3009: d+hu ti'i sgor tshud de'i yon tan //
NG0200:3010: rtsa rlung bsgoms pas d+hu tir rlung *//
NG0200:3011: tshud pas phyag rgya chen por 'char //
NG0200:3012: de bzhir d+hu tir rlung tshud tshe //
NG0200:3014: shugs kyis d+hu tir rlung tshud tshul //
NG0200:3015: pho mo bde ba spyad rjes su //
NG0200:3016: byang sems phebs tshe d+hu tir tshud //
NG0200:3017: dran med bde la sma mi shes //
NG0200:3018: de bzhin brgya lam 'chi khar yang *//
NG0200:3019: d+hu tir rlung tshud cang mi dran //
NG0200:3020: de phyir a wa d+hu ti ni //
NG0200:3021: mi rtog chos dbyings ye shes rtsa //
NG0200:3022: de nas rtsa gnas rim pa'o //
NG0200:3023: dpal gsang ba 'dus pa rgyud kyi rgyal po las //
NG0200:3024: lus la rtsa gnas yongs rdzogs bstan pa'i le'u ste
NG0200:3025: bcu bzhi pa'o // // de nas yang 'dus pa'i
NG0200:3026: 'khor rnams kyis mgrin gcig tu ston pa kun tu
NG0200:3027: bzang po dpal chen po che mchog he ru ka
NG0200:3028: la gsol pa / kye kye kye /
NG0200:3029: 'byung ba'i rang rtsal kun tu bzang *//
NG0200:3030: thabs chen rgyal po he ru ka / 'gyu byed stobs ldan rlung gi gnad //
NG0200:3031: bdag cag rnams la bka' stsol cig / de skad gsol ba'i don dgongs nas //
NG0200:3032: ston pa nyid kyis bka' stsal pa //
NG0200:3033: 'khor 'das bzang mo zab mo yang kun gzhi dang *//
NG0200:3034: ma rig 'gyu byed rlung dbang gis //
NG0200:3035: mnga' sgor khu khrag stor chags nas //
NG0200:3036: lo gcig zla ba bcu gnyis bar //
NG0200:3037: zhag re la ni rtsa'i bye brag / nyis brgya nyis brgya skyed 'phel bas //
NG0200:3038: stong phrag bdun bcu rtsa gnyis rtsa //
NG0200:3039: rim gyis chags shing de bskyed de //
NG0200:3040: rtsa yi gtso bo srog pa'i rtsa //
NG0200:3041: 'gyu ba rlung gis sems de grangs //
NG0200:3042: nyi khri chig stong rlung rgyus pas //
NG0200:3043: de las 'bras bu brgyad khri dang *//
NG0200:3044: bzhi stong dag tu rang shar cing *//
NG0200:3045: de nyid rnam grangs mang gis kyang *//
NG0200:3046: rtsa bar bsdus na sde brgyad de //
NG0200:3047: phyi rlung nang rlung gsang rlung @#//
NG0200:3049: rlung la nyams len goms rtags dang *//
NG0200:3050: gegs sel rlung gi yon tan no //
NG0200:3051: de yang phyi ni rlung brgyad de //
NG0200:3053: phung po 'jig rlung rgyun gcod rlung *//
NG0200:3054: 'byin byed rlung dang las byed rlung *//
NG0200:3055: 'bigs byed rlung dang khyab rlung ngo *//
NG0200:3056: nang ni yang ni rlung brgyad de //
NG0200:3057: gyen rgyu thur du sel ba'i rlung *//
NG0200:3058: dwangs snyigs 'byed rlung bkrag gzi skyed //
NG0200:3059: snying rje me dang me mnyam rlung *//
NG0200:3060: dwangs snyigs phyir 'byed shes rab rlung *//
NG0200:3061: gsang rlung kun gzhi byang chub sems //
NG0200:3062: rlung gis las ni zhag gcig la //
NG0200:3063: nyi khri dang ni chig stong rgyu //
NG0200:3064: bsdu na nyon mongs ye shes rlung *//
NG0200:3065: zhag re la yang rlung de gnyis //
NG0200:3066: khri tsho re dang lnga brgya rgyu //
NG0200:3068: rlung gsum dag tu 'dus pa yin //
NG0200:3069: 'byung ba'i rlung ni sor bcu drug / phyir 'byung
NG0200:3070: nang rlung sor bcu drug / nang 'jug gnas rlung
NG0200:3071: skad cig tsam // lte ba dag na gnas pa yin //
NG0200:3072: rlung la zhon nas yid 'gyu bas //
NG0200:3073: 'khor ba skyed byed rlung yang yin //
NG0200:3074: de phyir rigs drug rang la tshang *//
NG0200:3075: de nas rtsa rnams 'bri tshul yang *//
NG0200:3076: lo gcig lon nas lo brgya'i bar //
NG0200:3077: zhag re lon nas rtsa gnyis gnyis //
NG0200:3078: bri nas lo brgyas nus pa 'jig / de tshe rigs pa byang chub sems //
NG0200:3079: snying rje med pa'i rlung la zhon //
NG0200:3080: gsang ba nas thon dmyal bar skye //
NG0200:3081: rig pa thur rgyu'i rlung la zhon //
NG0200:3082: bshang lam nas thon yi dwags skye //
NG0200:3083: rigs pa me mnyam rlung la zhon //
NG0200:3084: lte ba nas thon byol song skye //
NG0200:3085: yang na rig pa byang chub sems //
NG0200:3086: bkrag dang gzi mdangs rlung la zhon //
NG0200:3087: mig g.yas nas thon lha gnas skye //
NG0200:3088: rig pa dwangs snyigs 'byed rlung zhon //
NG0200:3089: kha sna nas thon mi ru skye //
NG0200:3090: rigs pa phyir 'byed rlung la zhon //
NG0200:3091: ltag rtsa nas thon lha min skye //
NG0200:3092: yang ni rig pa byang chub sems //
NG0200:3093: gyen du rgyu ba'i rlung la zhon //
NG0200:3094: tshangs bug nas thon bcu gsum non //
NG0200:3095: rig pa shes rab rlung la zhon //
NG0200:3096: snying ga'i dbus nas ye shes lam //
NG0200:3097: mig g.yon 'bras bu rang ngo shes //
NG0200:3098: thams cad rang byung ye shes 'char //
NG0200:3099: de ltar rlung dang rig pa gnyis //
NG0200:3100: don byed gcig la mtshan nyid gnyis //
NG0200:3101: rang rig mtshan nyid dran zhing gsal //
NG0200:3102: rlung gi mtshan nyid bskyod 'khrugs sems kyang 'bebs //
NG0200:3103: de gnyis bsdang ba'i dper brjod ni //
NG0200:3105: rlung ni rta long rkang can 'dra //
NG0200:3106: de gnyis bsdongs pas phyogs bcur bgrod //
NG0200:3107: de phyir rnam shes rlung gis bskyod //
NG0200:3108: sgo lnga'i yul sogs kun tu rgyu //
NG0200:3109: rig pa'i rgyu dang rlung rkyen 'dzom //
NG0200:3110: 'khor ba'i bya ba thams cad byed //
NG0200:3111: mi rta bral na 'gro rgyu med //
NG0200:3112: de bzhin lam gyi rnal 'byor pas //
NG0200:3113: d+hu tir rlung bzung bsgom pa'i tshe //
NG0200:3115: rig pa rlung med g.yo 'gul med //
NG0200:3118: mig med rta pho dang 'dra ba'i //
NG0200:3119: spyod byed rlung rta rig med pa'i //
NG0200:3120: 'gro bar mi nus rang dbang thob //
NG0200:3121: de tshe yang dag rang ngo sprod //
NG0200:3122: rlung rig rang dwangs der sangs rgya'o //
NG0200:3123: de phyir rlung 'dzin nyams len ni //
NG0200:3124: sngon du tshogs bsag bla ma mchod //
NG0200:3125: bgegs bsrung skyabs 'gro sems bskyed bya //
NG0200:3126: khams gso bcud kyi sman mar sbyar //
NG0200:3127: dngos gzhi'i dus su 'brel mtshams gcad //
NG0200:3128: dben par 'bol ba'i stan la 'dug / lha gsal nga rgyal mos pa bya //
NG0200:3129: rkang pa rdo rje skyil krung bca' //
NG0200:3130: sgal tshigs gser gyi dong tse bsrang *//
NG0200:3131: seng ltar stod 'gyings yid dgyer bya //
NG0200:3132: rma bya'i mgrin bzhin yid dgug pa //
NG0200:3133: lag gnyis mnyam gzhag lder tsho 'dra //
NG0200:3134: mig 'bras sna yi rtse la dbab //
NG0200:3135: lus gnad drug la legs goms nas //
NG0200:3137: rngub bskyil 'phang dang bskor bas te //
NG0200:3138: bde gshegs rnams kyi yang snying mchog / rngub rlung om la bskyil gnas ah //
NG0200:3139: 'phang ba hum yin rlung gsum gyi //
NG0200:3140: gnas pa ahla zin nan bskyed //
NG0200:3141: 'khor lo bskor ba gang zhe na //
NG0200:3142: sna bug g.yas nas rlung rgyu tshe //
NG0200:3143: thabs rlung nyon mongs rlung yin phyir //
NG0200:3144: mi bzung bzung na rlung log 'ong *//
NG0200:3145: sna bug g.yon nas rgyu ba'i tshe //
NG0200:3146: shes rab ye shes rlung yin phyir //
NG0200:3147: bzung na skyon med nyams rtogs 'phel //
NG0200:3148: sna bug gnyis nas mnyam rgyu'i tshe //
NG0200:3149: thabs shes gnyis su med pa'i rlung *//
NG0200:3150: a wa d+hu ti'i sgor tshud pas //
NG0200:3152: de phyir rlung bzung gnad 'di ste //
NG0200:3153: gru gu 'chams pos bshang sgo bsdam //
NG0200:3155: hum ring gsum gyis rlung dug phyung *//
NG0200:3156: 'og rlung bsdams te steng rlung ni //
NG0200:3157: rngub cing mnan te bskyil bar bya //
NG0200:3158: tshad du slebs tshe mda' ltar du //
NG0200:3159: sna nas mnga' gang tshad du 'phang *//
NG0200:3160: yang rngub yang bskyil yang 'phangs te //
NG0200:3161: gnas pa'i rlung de bskyil yun bsring *//
NG0200:3162: 'byongs tshe d+hu tir rlung tshud nas //
NG0200:3163: skyod byed rlung rta g.yo 'gul bral //
NG0200:3165: de tshe rlung nyid las rung bas //
NG0200:3166: tha mal shes pa snying dbus sad //
NG0200:3167: chos rnams kun gyi de bzhin nyid //
NG0200:3168: ma bcos byang chub sems rtogs pas //
NG0200:3169: nyon mongs rang sangs ye shes rgyas //
NG0200:3170: gsang rlung ngos zin ngo mtshar che //
NG0200:3171: de ltar klung bsgoms 'byongs rtags gsum //
NG0200:3172: phyi dang nang dang gsang ba'i tshul //
NG0200:3175: nang rtags snang ba sgyu mar rtogs //
NG0200:3177: lto gos ched med la sogs 'byung *//
NG0200:3178: gsang rtags bde gsal 'dzin pa med //
NG0200:3179: ma bcos bde chen 'gyur med brtan //
NG0200:3180: rdo rje lta bu'i ting 'dzin no //
NG0200:3181: bla ma'i man ngag ma thob na //
NG0200:3184: mdor na rngub dgang 'phen la sogs //
NG0200:3185: gtong ran bzung tshad ma shes shing *//
NG0200:3186: 'khor lo'i go rim log kyang gegs //
NG0200:3188: shor ba srid na smyo nas 'gro //
NG0200:3189: sha mdangs bar du rlung shor na //
NG0200:3191: snying la shor na snying rlung 'byung *//
NG0200:3192: thur rlung log na phyi sa dang *//
NG0200:3193: byang sems dkar dmar 'dzag pa yin //
NG0200:3194: gyen du log na mgo 'khor zhing *//
NG0200:3196: de sogs rlung skyon bsam yas kyang *//
NG0200:3197: mun la nyi bzhin dug sel thabs //
NG0200:3198: rlung bsgom thun mtshams thams cad du //
NG0200:3199: hum ring gsum bus rjes su //
NG0200:3200: ha drag yang yang bstud cing gdab //
NG0200:3201: ro stod yang snyam sems na gzhag / des ni rlung skyon 'ong mi srid //
NG0200:3202: chig chod thabs kyi rgyal po yin //
NG0200:3203: de ltar gegs bsal rlung bsgoms pas //
NG0200:3204: yon tan mngon shes rnam drug dang *//
NG0200:3205: spyan lnga chags pa med pa 'byung *//
NG0200:3206: sems ma zin pa zin par 'gyur //
NG0200:3207: zin pa brtan gyur rig rtsal sbyang *//
NG0200:3209: chu la mi 'bying brag rjes thon //
NG0200:3210: rkang mgyogs lha srin bran du 'khol //
NG0200:3211: rang rig rtsal dbang nges par 'thob //
NG0200:3212: tshe dbang rig 'dzin la sogs pa'i //
NG0200:3213: yon tan brjod kyis mi lang ngo *//
NG0200:3215: dpal gsang ba 'dus pa rgyud kyi rgyal po las /
NG0200:3216: 'gyu byed stobs ldan rlung gnad yongs rdzogs bstan pa'i
NG0200:3217: le'u ste bco lnga pa'o // // de nas 'dus
NG0200:3219: mgrin gcig tu ston pa kun tu bzang po dpal che mchog he ru ka la gsol pa /
NG0200:3221: thig le chen po kun tu bzang *//
NG0200:3222: byams chen rgyal po he ru ka / thig le byang sems gtum mo'i gnad //
NG0200:3223: bdag cag rnams la bka' stsol mdzod //
NG0200:3224: de skad gsol ba'i don dgongs nas //
NG0200:3225: ston pa nyid kyis bka' stsal pa //
NG0200:3226: byang sems thig le'i man ngag gnad //
NG0200:3227: gsang sngags grol lam rgyu yin cing *//
NG0200:3228: thabs lam kun gyi mthar thug yin //
NG0200:3229: rtsa gnas lus la rab brten pa'i //
NG0200:3230: byang sems stong phrag bye ba dang *//
NG0200:3231: phyed dang bzhi brgya yod na yang *//
NG0200:3232: bsdu na dwangs snyigs srog 'dzin gsum //
NG0200:3233: dwangs ma las gyur byang sems ni //
NG0200:3234: bza' btung bcud zos dwangs 'gyur tshul //
NG0200:3235: zhag bdun lon nas chu ser 'gyur //
NG0200:3236: bdun phrag sha la bdun na tshil //
NG0200:3237: bdun phrag bzhi na rkang mar 'gyur //
NG0200:3238: bdun lnga rgyungs pa bdun drug klad //
NG0200:3239: de nas bdun na byang chub sems //
NG0200:3240: thig le dkar po nyid du 'gyur //
NG0200:3241: byang chub sems kyi snyigs ma ni //
NG0200:3242: ngar snabs lud pa la sogs yin //
NG0200:3243: srog 'dzin pa yi byang sems ni //
NG0200:3244: snying dbus khrag gi dwangs ma ste //
NG0200:3245: byi'u len ma'i sgong tshad kyi //
NG0200:3246: dkyil nang 'od kyi gong bu ni //
NG0200:3247: sran ma'i ga'u kha sbyar tshad //
NG0200:3250: de ltar gnas lugs legs shes nas //
NG0200:3251: de nyid nyams len gal che ste //
NG0200:3252: lus la rtsa gnas rtsa nang na //
NG0200:3253: byang sems gnas te de zhu nas //
NG0200:3255: de phyir byang sems 'ju ba'i las //
NG0200:3256: gtum mo nyid ces de la lnga //
NG0200:3259: phyi ni rdzas kyi gtum mo bstan //
NG0200:3260: g.yag rgod mkhris pa dron mo ru //
NG0200:3261: sga skya pi ling pho ba ris //
NG0200:3262: tshwa sna tshogs chad zhib btags bsrub //
NG0200:3263: skam thag chod par mnyes zin nas /
NG0200:3264: bu ram mgo bsdus sran tshad dril //
NG0200:3265: sran tshad gsum gyis zhag gcig dros //
NG0200:3266: drod bul srid na sga dmar sbyar //
NG0200:3267: bsku mnye byas pas ser spongs te //
NG0200:3268: bde drod me ltar 'bar bar nges //
NG0200:3269: nang ni bskyed rim gtum mos te //
NG0200:3270: me dbang thob pa'i rnal 'byor pas //
NG0200:3271: lus ni lha yi gzhal yas khang *//
NG0200:3272: sgong skogs lta bu'i stong ra bsgom //
NG0200:3273: nang khrol med par dmar sang de //
NG0200:3274: rgya rdza mer bsregs lta bur bsgom //
NG0200:3275: sems nyid che mchog phyag rgya rkyang *//
NG0200:3276: me ri'i klong na bzhugs par bsgom //
NG0200:3277: ngag gis om ahhum dang gsum //
NG0200:3278: rdo rje'i bzlas pa yid kyis bya //
NG0200:3279: lus bde ngag nus sems rtogs pas //
NG0200:3280: sgo gsum bde drod 'bar bar nges //
NG0200:3281: gsang ba rlung bzung gtum mo ni //
NG0200:3284: bde ba'i gdan la tsog pur 'dug / rkang g.yon bol gong g.yas mthing mnan //
NG0200:3286: g.yas g.yon bsnol ba'i lag mgo yis //
NG0200:3287: bar lhu gnyis kyis 'phar rtsa bsdam //
NG0200:3288: de khongs pus mo gnyis po bsdam //
NG0200:3289: brla chen nang sha spo kyang spe sha dang *//
NG0200:3290: rtsa bo che bzhi cha bsgrims la //
NG0200:3291: sems klong me yi 'khor lo bskor //
NG0200:3292: ro stod g.yas su bskor cing bzhu //
NG0200:3293: seng gis g.yengs pas rtsa mig dgram //
NG0200:3295: lte ba'i lkog na me'i sa bon //
NG0200:3296: ram gnas de la ram brjod pas //
NG0200:3299: yid gsal ma yengs ngar dang bcas //
NG0200:3301: khyab byed bar gyi rlung dkrugs te //
NG0200:3302: a long kha ni nem tsam bsdams //
NG0200:3303: rang lus rdo rjer gsal ba yi //
NG0200:3304: lte ba bde bas gang ba la //
NG0200:3305: lus byings me ru 'bar bar bsgom //
NG0200:3306: dug dbyung gegs sel rlung dang mtshungs //
NG0200:3307: rlung nyid las rung drod sbar bas //
NG0200:3308: thig le zhu nas bde drod 'bar //
NG0200:3310: steng 'og gnyis kyi rlung yang ni //
NG0200:3311: ha cang bsdams drags ma yin te //
NG0200:3312: skabs su gsang zhing mtshams par mnan //
NG0200:3313: steng rlung thabs kyi rang bzhin las //
NG0200:3315: 'og rlung shes rab rang bzhin nyid //
NG0200:3318: lte ba sprul pa'i 'khor lo ru //
NG0200:3321: don dam gtum mo rgya khab tsam //
NG0200:3322: dmar gsal gyen du 'bar ba yis //
NG0200:3323: rtsa bar ram dmar gcig tu gnas //
NG0200:3324: rang nyid lus kyi stong ra ni //
NG0200:3325: rdza bsregs thur la sbub pa 'dra //
NG0200:3326: gsang gnas yi ge yam dkar las //
NG0200:3328: don dam tsan+da li la phog / ram nyid me 'bar lte ba yis //
NG0200:3330: de rtags lus ni bem bem byed //
NG0200:3331: sems kyang bag tsam gnas pa 'byung *//
NG0200:3332: de nas me nyid snying gang sleb //
NG0200:3334: phung po lnga yi rtog pa dang *//
NG0200:3335: dug lnga bsregs pas bde drod 'bar //
NG0200:3337: de nas me lce mgrin par sleb //
NG0200:3338: de rtags dgod dang a i zer //
NG0200:3339: de nas me lce klad dkyil drang *//
NG0200:3340: klad pa bde chen 'khor lo dros //
NG0200:3341: lte ba'i thig le byang chub sems //
NG0200:3342: ham mgo thur la bstan pa de //
NG0200:3343: 'od du ltem gyis zhu nas kyang *//
NG0200:3344: byang sems thig le bcu drug 'dzag / de las bde chen skye tshul ni //
NG0200:3345: klad dkyil babs pas dga' ba skye //
NG0200:3346: de phyir mgrin pa'i 'khor lo 'dzag / de yis bde ba mchog dga' skye //
NG0200:3347: de phyir snying gar bzhi 'dzag pas //
NG0200:3348: dga' bral bde stong dga' ba skye //
NG0200:3349: de phyir lte dbus gnyis 'dzag pas //
NG0200:3350: lus med bsam pa'i bde ba skye //
NG0200:3351: bde stong dbyer med bde ba'i mchog / lhan skyes ye shes dga' ba skye //
NG0200:3353: de nyid ngos bzung bsgom byas na //
NG0200:3355: thig le byang sems ngo sprad gsum //
NG0200:3356: sems bzung ngo sprod zhen bzlog ste //
NG0200:3357: dang po byang sems gzung thabs ni //
NG0200:3358: spyi gtsug bde chen 'khor lor om //
NG0200:3359: mgrin pa longs spyod 'khor lor ah //
NG0200:3360: snying ga chos kyi 'khor lor hum //
NG0200:3361: lte ba sprul pa'i 'khor lor ham //
NG0200:3362: byang sems 'khor lor bsgom pa yam //
NG0200:3363: de las 'od zer gyen du sdud //
NG0200:3364: 'khor lo bzhi yi yi ge bzhi //
NG0200:3366: de la sems gtad mi 'phro na //
NG0200:3367: snying gar drag tu gtad la bzung *//
NG0200:3369: dar cig glod la rjes ngos gzung *//
NG0200:3370: rang rig sprin med bar snang bzhin //
NG0200:3371: dngas la gsal ba rang sor zhog / me long nang gi gzugs brnyan ltar //
NG0200:3372: sal le hrig ge 'dzin med zhog / de nyid ngo sprod bstan pa ni //
NG0200:3373: de ltar srog 'dzin byang chub sems //
NG0200:3374: bde stong tsit+ta'i dbus su bsad sad kyang *//
NG0200:3375: thams cad ye shes rtsal du shes //
NG0200:3376: lhan skyes ye shes ngos zin tshe //
NG0200:3377: shes pa bde gsal mi rtog gsum //
