NG0200:3831: phur pa'i bye brag rnam pa bzhi //
NG0200:3832: yongs rdzogs dpal gyi sku bskyed de //
NG0200:3833: sku gsung thugs su byin gyis brlab //
NG0200:3834: ye shes lnga dang rdzas dbang bskur //
NG0200:3835: 'debs mkhan gdab yul tshe khrus lung *//
NG0200:3836: gdab dang thebs tshad 'bras bu ste //
NG0200:3837: phur pa ngo bos stong shes kyi //
NG0200:3838: ngang las yongs rdzogs dpal chen bskyed //
NG0200:3839: de las sprul pas dgra bgegs dgug / phur pa'i lha rnams sgo gsum du //
NG0200:3840: om dkar ahdmar hum mthing bsgom //
NG0200:3841: de nas phur pa'i spyi gtsug dang *//
NG0200:3842: mgrin pa snying ga lte gsang du //
NG0200:3843: 'bru lnga rigs lnga bskyed la bzhag / de ni ye shes phur pa ste //
NG0200:3844: kun gyis ma rig snying re rje //
NG0200:3845: log lta rnams la snying rje bskyed //
NG0200:3846: gnyis med sgrol ba'i snying rje bsgom //
NG0200:3847: de ni snying rje'i phur pa ste //
NG0200:3848: rang nyid lhar gsal phyag g.yas g.yon //
NG0200:3849: rigs lnga khrag 'thung yab yum bskyed //
NG0200:3850: phur pa byang chub sems su bsgril //
NG0200:3851: de ni byang sems phur pa yin //
NG0200:3852: phur pa de la nyung dkar 'dril //
NG0200:3853: gu gul bdug cing dug khrag byug / 'bar ba e yi gdan la bzhugs //
NG0200:3854: mtshan ma rdzas kyi phur pa yin //
NG0200:3855: de nas bskyed rdzogs gzhung bsrangs te //
NG0200:3856: 'dzab bzlas rtags la sbyar cing bsgrub //
NG0200:3857: bdag nyid lta spyod zung 'jug pas //
NG0200:3858: phur pa 'dril shing drag sngags bzlas //
NG0200:3859: gdab yul dgra bgegs log lta can //
NG0200:3860: gzugs la brten nas dngos gsal gdab //
NG0200:3861: kho yi rnam shes srog dngos po //
NG0200:3862: snying nag khrag dwangs bye'u mgo tsam //
NG0200:3863: de dbus a 'od thig le'i nang *//
NG0200:3864: nr-i ljang gcig yod gdab pa'i yul //
NG0200:3865: de nas phur rtse hum gsum dang *//
NG0200:3866: rtse sgab dag tu phat gsum bsam //
NG0200:3867: ngag tu drag sngags dgu bzlas shing *//
NG0200:3869: nr-i dang ar bcas phur rtse yi //
NG0200:3870: hum la 'dus nas a dkar gsal //
NG0200:3871: rang la bstan pas de tshur 'dus //
NG0200:3872: de ni tshe lung dgongs pa yin //
NG0200:3873: de nas dgra srog dug gsum gyi //
NG0200:3874: ngo bo hum gsum gnas pa de //
NG0200:3875: zur gyi phat gsum gyis 'phangs te //
NG0200:3876: 'og min dpal gyi thugs kar spros //
NG0200:3877: hum nyid 'od zhu mgrin pa yi //
NG0200:3878: a la thim nas a yang zhu //
NG0200:3879: dung khang om thim om 'od zhu //
NG0200:3880: sgal tshigs la brgyud yum mkhar babs //
NG0200:3881: rgyal ba'i sras su byas pas ni //
NG0200:3882: gnas spar zab mo khrus lung yin //
NG0200:3883: de nas gnas dgur dpa' dgus gdab //
NG0200:3884: tshogs brgyad bsgral zhing sgo lnga chod //
NG0200:3885: gdab phur kun gyis khyab par gdab //
NG0200:3886: de bar drag sngags phur tshugs bzlas //
NG0200:3889: phur re thebs tshad 'bras bu yang *//
NG0200:3890: gdab phur 'ben gsum grub mtha' gcig / thams cad chos dbyings stong par bsgral //
NG0200:3891: rig pa ye shes phur pa de //
NG0200:3892: chos dbyings thebs pas chos kyi sku //
NG0200:3893: tshad med snying rje'i phur pa de //
NG0200:3895: byang chub sems kyi phur pa de //
NG0200:3896: yum mkhar thebs pas longs sku 'thob //
NG0200:3897: mtshan ma rdzas kyi phur pa des //
NG0200:3898: dgra bgegs la btab bstan pa tshugs //
NG0200:3899: drag sngags rgyal po gnam thog 'di //
NG0200:3900: gar dgos las la sbyar ba ni //
NG0200:3901: gtor na gtang dang srung ba'i mkhar //
NG0200:3902: chos skyong bskul gcun dgra bgegs bsgral //
NG0200:3903: bgegs dpung gzhom dang klu nad 'dul //
NG0200:3904: smyo 'bog 'dul dang rbod gtong bzlog / bgegs rnams gzir dang zho chang bsrung *//
NG0200:3905: mdze nad gso dang gag lhog gzhom //
NG0200:3907: om ahhum i dam ba lim ta sarba pany+tsa a mr-i ta kha hi /
NG0200:3909: ma ha ba lim kha hi /
NG0200:3910: ka ya waka tsit+ta rak+sha rak+sha ku ru hum /
NG0200:3913: badzra sarba dush+tan trig nan e hur thum dzahma ra ya rbad /
NG0200:3914: nr-i sha trum hur thum dzahma ra ya rbad /
NG0200:3915: dgra bgegs dam sri ni tri rbad thum dza /
NG0200:3920: da ra ya da ra ya /
NG0200:3921: hum ha he phat b+h+yo hri ta ya /
NG0200:3923: pra ha ra na hum phat /
NG0200:3924: sa ma ya a ti pra ma na /
NG0200:3925: ma ra ni b+h+yo a la la b+h+yo a la la b+h+yo /
NG0200:3926: bzlog bzlog / sham bu'i drag sngags de dag gis //
NG0200:3927: las kyi bye brag thams cad 'grub //
NG0200:3929: dpal gsang ba 'dus pa rgyud kyi rgyal po las /
NG0200:3930: bde gshegs yongs rdzogs phur sgrub kyi le'u ste bcu
NG0200:3931: dgu pa'o // // de nas yang 'dus pa'i 'khor
NG0200:3933: ston pa dpal kun tu bzang po dpal che mchog he ru ka la gsol pa /
NG0200:3935: yon tan bdag nyid kun tu bzang *//
NG0200:3936: bdud rtsi 'khyil ba he ru ka / dam rdzas sman gyi bsgrub pa gang *//
NG0200:3937: bdag cag rnams la bka' stsol cig / de skad gsol pa'i don dgongs nas //
NG0200:3938: ston pa nyid kyis bka' stsal pa //
NG0200:3940: thams cad bdud rtsi'i rang bzhin la //
NG0200:3941: rang gar rnam rtog ma choms na //
NG0200:3942: sarba sman gyi sgrub pa bstan //
NG0200:3943: 'di yang sgrub chen khog nas dbyung *//
NG0200:3944: thog mar khol bu'i bsgrub pa la //
NG0200:3945: mtshan ldan thod pa kha sbyar nang *//
NG0200:3946: sman rnams yongs rdzogs rigs brgyas gang yang lngar sbyar //
NG0200:3947: 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi mu khyud bcas //
NG0200:3948: dri chen glang sha dza ti shar //
NG0200:3949: byang sems seng sha bzang drug dbus /
NG0200:3950: sha chen rta sha ka kol lho //
NG0200:3951: pad+ma'i rak+ta rma bya li shi nub //
NG0200:3952: dri chu khyung sha gur gum byang *//
NG0200:3953: gzhan yang ga pur a bar skyur //
NG0200:3954: thal ka rdo rje a ga ru //
NG0200:3955: du ru ka dang snying sna'i tshogs //
NG0200:3958: tsan dan rgun 'brum star bu dang *//
NG0200:3959: lce pog la sogs sman rnyed tshad //
NG0200:3960: rtsa lo me tog 'bras bu dgod //
NG0200:3961: cong zhi shug 'bru+u mkhan pa mtshe //
NG0200:3962: dkar gsum mngar gsum la sogs bsag / sman du gyur pa kun gyis bskor //
NG0200:3963: chang chu 'o ma rin chen bsham //
NG0200:3964: yon tan rgyas grub yin pa'i phyir //
NG0200:3965: yur ba chu rtsa lug ru ser //
NG0200:3966: gi wam 'od ldan skyobs su bsag / gzung thag
NG0200:3967: btags la dar gur dbug / las kyi gzhung bsrang
NG0200:3968: tshogs 'khor bya // bdag nyid yongs rdzogs skur bsgoms te /
NG0200:3970: kam las thod sgyed bum pa dgal //
NG0200:3971: yam las rlung byung ram me sbar //
NG0200:3972: dam rdzas sha lnga bdud rtsi lnga //
NG0200:3975: de nyid brgya rtsa brgyad brjod pas //
NG0200:3976: phyag 'tshal lngar gyur de nyid las //
NG0200:3977: rigs lnga yab yum bcur gyur nas //
NG0200:3978: sbyor mdzad byang sems bdud rtsir gyur //
NG0200:3979: snang srid thams cad de ltar gsal //
NG0200:3982: spros la dga' na rigs brgya'am //
NG0200:3983: thams cad rigs lnga'i ngo bor bsam //
NG0200:3984: spros la mi dga' rdo rje sems //
NG0200:3985: rigs gcig kho na'i ngo bor bsgrub //
NG0200:3986: rtsa sngags bsnyen rjes sngags 'di bzlas //
NG0200:3988: sarba pany+tsa a mr-i ta ra sa ya na ta na /
NG0200:3989: dza ya gu h+ya sid+d+hi hum hrihtha /
NG0200:3990: drang srong rnams la gsol ba gdab //
NG0200:3991: khrol bu zhag gsum tshar rjes su //
NG0200:3992: gong gi rigs lnga 'od du zhu //
NG0200:3993: gnyis med bdud rtsi'i ngang du sbyar //
NG0200:3994: thams cad gnyis med sems dpa' bsgom //
NG0200:3995: om sarba pany+tsa a mr-i ta badzra tsit+ta sa ma ya hum /
NG0200:3996: mkha' gsang bdud rtsi bskyil cir dbab //
NG0200:3997: mchod bstod dngos grub blang gis bsdu //
NG0200:3998: thabs shes mnyam pa nyid du sbyang */
NG0200:3999: zhing steng gtun bzhag yab yum sbyar //
NG0200:4001: sarba pany+tsa a mr-i ta kun+da li ha na ha na hum phat /
NG0200:4002: sman rnams btags btsag bdud rtsir sbal //
NG0200:4003: thod par blugs te rgyas gdab dril //
NG0200:4004: mtshams bcad nyul le drag tu bskrad //
NG0200:4005: yi ge lnga yis sngar bzhin sbyang *//
NG0200:4006: yum gyis pho brang yab la 'bul /
NG0200:4007: gzungs thag bzung zhing dkyil 'khor bskyed //
NG0200:4008: las gzhung tshogs 'khor dus drug bya //
NG0200:4009: dkyil 'khor bdun brtseg bsgom pa yi //
NG0200:4010: ting 'dzin sngar dang mtshungs pa las //
NG0200:4011: bdud rtsi'i dkyil du bcud 'dus pas //
NG0200:4012: khro rgyal dpal chen yongs rdzogs pa //
NG0200:4013: che mchog bdud rtsi 'khyil ba'i sku /
NG0200:4014: ljang ser zhal gcig phyag gnyis ni //
NG0200:4015: yum la 'khyud nas thal mo bzed //
NG0200:4016: ye shes bdud rtsi'i bum pa 'dzin //
NG0200:4017: yab yum sbyor ba'i sbyor mtshams nas //
NG0200:4018: ye shes bdud rtsi phab nas bskyil //
NG0200:4019: om ahhum sarba pany+tsa a mr-i ta kun+da li hum hrihtha /
NG0200:4020: gsol 'debs tshig gis skabs skabs bskul //
NG0200:4021: drang srong spyan drangs gsol 'debs ni //
NG0200:4022: hum tshangs pa dag gi gtso bo mchog / dung gi thor tshugs khong gseng @#//
NG0200:4024: tshangs pa kun sgrol chen po dang */
NG0200:4025: drang srong chen po ljang sngon dang *//
NG0200:4026: tsa ra ka dang nabs so skyes //
NG0200:4027: tha skar bu dang lha skyabs dang *//
NG0200:4028: rgyun shes dang ni g.yon phyogs lha //
NG0200:4029: thang la gnas dang me bzhin 'jug / rkang gnyis spyod dang ka ya na //
NG0200:4030: sher khyer dang ni ljang sngon bu //
NG0200:4031: nyi ma zla ba klu ru bcas //
NG0200:4032: bram ze gzhon nu'i sprin dang ni //
NG0200:4033: rin po che dang go de shan //
NG0200:4034: gzhon nu srid dang 'gro skyobs dang *//
NG0200:4035: rtsibs kyi mu khyud 'dzin la sogs //
NG0200:4036: khyed cag 'khor dang bcas pa yis //
NG0200:4037: sngon chad bsgrubs nas grub pa sbyin //
NG0200:4038: yon tan bdud rtsi'i sid+d+hi stsol //
NG0200:4039: zhes pa dus drug gsol ba gdab //
NG0200:4040: de tshe grub rtags gzugs sgra 'od //
NG0200:4041: dri chen du ba mang du 'phel //
NG0200:4042: rloms sems mi bskyed dngos grub blang *//
NG0200:4043: de nas gang bu zhag gcig bsgrub //
NG0200:4044: spog pa'i cho ga dag kyang bya //
NG0200:4046: rtsa sngags stong bzlas dngos grub blangs //
NG0200:4048: sarba pany+tsa a mr-i ta ka ya sid+d+hi om /
NG0200:4049: waka sid+d+hi am tsit+ta sid+d+hi hum /
NG0200:4051: drang srong gsol ba gdab rjes la //
NG0200:4053: rigs lnga yab yum mkha' klong du //
NG0200:4054: thabs dang shes rab sbyor ba las //
NG0200:4056: snang srid rtsi bcud sman rnams ni //
NG0200:4057: thams cad dag pas bdud rtsi che //
NG0200:4058: bdud rtsi lnga ru ye sangs rgyas //
NG0200:4059: bse phor dmar po mdzes pa dang *//
NG0200:4060: shel phor dkar po dri med mdzes //
NG0200:4061: bdud rtsi lnga yi bcud blugs te //
NG0200:4062: dam rdzas bdud rtsi'i chu 'di ni //
NG0200:4063: ye shes lha la phul ba'i tshe //
NG0200:4064: rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor thams cad mnyes //
NG0200:4065: dam can rnams la mchod pa yis //
NG0200:4066: srung ma rnams kyi thugs dam bskang *//
NG0200:4067: rig 'dzin rnams la phul ba'i tshe //
NG0200:4068: dngos grub rgya mtsho thams cad ster //
NG0200:4069: rnal 'byor bdag nyid myong ba'i tshe //
NG0200:4070: dbang dang dngos grub yongs su rdzogs //
NG0200:4071: bdud dang bgegs la phogs pa'i tshe //
NG0200:4072: lus sems thal ba rdul du brlag / e ma ho //
NG0200:4073: dam rdzas bdud rtsi'i chu 'di ni //
NG0200:4074: 'thong ngam thos sam reg pas kyang *//
NG0200:4075: thams cad dbang phyug bdag gis thob //
NG0200:4076: e ma thabs chen khyad par che //
NG0200:4077: e ma thabs chen bla na med //
NG0200:4078: e ma ngo mtshar rmad byung ba //
NG0200:4079: lta ba rmad byung ngo mtshar che //
NG0200:4080: spyod pa rmad byung ngo mtshar che //
NG0200:4081: nyon mongs ma spangs ngo mtshar che //
NG0200:4082: ye shes lnga rdzogs ngo mtshar che //
NG0200:4083: sku lnga lhun grub ngo mtshar che //
NG0200:4084: chos sku gcig la tha dad pa //
NG0200:4085: rigs lnga'i dngos grub 'dir thob bo //
NG0200:4086: yang dag 'chi med don brnyes so //
NG0200:4087: zhes brjod lha rnams bdud rtsir zhu //
NG0200:4088: bum gcig rdzas dbang bskur bya zhing *//
NG0200:4089: bde gshegs yongs rdzogs sman mchod bya //
NG0200:4090: lce thog lan bdun dngos grub blang *//
NG0200:4091: rjes su bdud rtsi 'khyil pa bskyed //
NG0200:4092: rin chen ga 'ur gter du stsal //
NG0200:4095: rtog pa ye shes sman sbyar pas //
NG0200:4096: dug lnga sman gyur ye shes spyod //
NG0200:4097: mnyam nyid rtogs pas yon tan rdzogs //
NG0200:4098: rang byung rnam dag yon tan mchog / dam rdzas bdud rtsi rtsa ba lnga //
NG0200:4099: rang lugs spyad dam bsgrub na mchog / rnam snang bdud rtsi phun tshogs gtso //
NG0200:4100: spyi dang bye brag so so ste //
NG0200:4101: rgyal blon 'khor tshogs phyi nang gsang *//
NG0200:4102: las tshogs dam bsrungs gags bsal na //
NG0200:4103: yon tan 'bras bu thun mong rdzogs //
NG0200:4104: rjes kyi cho ga sgrub chen bzhin //
NG0200:4107: dpal gsang ba 'dus pa rgyud kyi rgyal po las /
NG0200:4108: dam rdzas yongs rdzogs bdud rtsi sman sgrub kyi le'u
NG0200:4109: ste nyi shu pa'o // // de nas yang 'dus
NG0200:4110: pa'i 'khor rnams kyis mgrin gcig tu ston pa dpal
NG0200:4111: kun tu bzang po che mchog he ru ka la
NG0200:4113: mi rtog rtog bral kun tu bzang *//
NG0200:4114: dngos grub kun 'byung he ru ka / dngos grub rdzas chen bam sgrub thabs //
NG0200:4115: bdag cag rnams la bka' stsol cig / de skad gsol pa'i don dgongs te //
NG0200:4116: ston pa nyid kyis bka' stsal pa //
NG0200:4117: dpa' gtum nus pa ldan kun nyon //
NG0200:4118: gzigs stangs lnga yi sgo nas bsgrubs //
NG0200:4119: thugs rje'i yul dang slob ma dang *//
NG0200:4120: lha dang ru dra mchod rdzas so //
NG0200:4121: mchod rdzas dngos grub mchog sgrub ni //
NG0200:4122: ngan song gnas nas drang bsams pas //
NG0200:4123: dngos grub 'byung ba'i bam brtags te //
NG0200:4124: spang dang blang ba'i bam rigs gnyis //
NG0200:4125: spangs pa dam tshig spun grogs dang *//
NG0200:4127: spyi mched chos rigs kun kyang spangs //
NG0200:4128: lnga 'das la sogs dam nyams spang *//
NG0200:4129: blang bya pho mo gang yang rung *//
NG0200:4130: rigs bzang rtsa lnga man chod lon //
NG0200:4131: dngos grub ya mtshan chen po'i rdzas //
NG0200:4132: skye ba bdun pa'i bam ni rab //
NG0200:4133: rigs bzang bkra shis thum shi ba'i //
NG0200:4134: na gzhon gtsang ma'i bam ni 'bring *//
NG0200:4135: so bdun byis pa yin kyang blangs //
NG0200:4136: len tshe sngags g.yog blo brtan pas //
NG0200:4137: rang lus yongs rdzogs lhar gsal gdab //
NG0200:4138: rjes bzung dngos grub len bsam 'gro //
NG0200:4139: rigs 'dzin dam can grogs su khrid //
NG0200:4141: bgegs bskrad phyogs bskor ro gshed mnan //
NG0200:4142: sgor blangs nyung phur dud pas gzir //
NG0200:4143: yongs rdzogs bro yis rab tu gdul //
NG0200:4144: 'dag chal sug chu'i khrus kyis bkrus //
NG0200:4145: snying rjes rigs drug gnas nas drang *//
NG0200:4146: de nas dkyil 'khor sgrub rdzas rnams //
NG0200:4147: gsang ba'i sgrub chen gong bzhin bshams //
NG0200:4148: bskyed rdzogs mchod bstod rdzogs rjes su //
NG0200:4149: bum tshigs rkang 'di med pa'ang 'dug dbang phan dang nus dbang bskur //
NG0200:4150: ro de slob mar shes bya ste //
NG0200:4151: dbang stegs khar bzhag dkyil 'khor du //
NG0200:4152: 'jug dang rjes gnang me tog dor //
NG0200:4155: dkyil 'khor dbus bzhag rgyan spras te //
NG0200:4156: spros la dga' bas gnas dgu ru //
NG0200:4158: yang na spyi gtsug mgrin pa dang *//
NG0200:4159: snying ga lte dbus gsang gnas su //
NG0200:4160: rigs lnga'i srog snying 'bru lnga bsam //
NG0200:4162: lha tshogs la thim thugs dam bskang *//
NG0200:4163: lha las 'od 'phros phyi nang gi / bdud rtsi bkug nas rigs lnga yis //
NG0200:4164: nang du spro zhing dgyes pa bskyed //
NG0200:4165: ye shes chen po'i bcud tshur la //
NG0200:4166: bam la thim pas dngos grub thob //
NG0200:4167: 'od byung bdag gi snying gar thim //
NG0200:4168: dngos grub yongs rdzogs thob bsam zhing *//
NG0200:4169: rtsa sngags sham bur 'di btags bzlas //
NG0200:4173: sam ha ra na hum ah /
NG0200:4174: stong stong bzlas shing stong tshig tu //
NG0200:4175: bskang gso'i cho ga rgyas par bya //
NG0200:4176: rjes la lha bsdu dngos grub blang *//
NG0200:4177: de nas bam de byang shar bzhag / dgra bgegs ru dra bstim la bsgral //
NG0200:4178: rgyab nas thig gdab rgyab nas bshu //
NG0200:4179: gsil te rat+na'i gzhong pa ru //
NG0200:4180: mgo dang sgal rus srog rtsa dbus //
NG0200:4181: snying shar go ro tsa na lho //
NG0200:4182: lce nub lto ba byang du dgod //
NG0200:4183: gsang ba shar lho rgyab lho nub //
NG0200:4184: nub byang brla g.yas rtsa chen la //
NG0200:4185: byang shar rtsa chen g.yon pa 'god //
NG0200:4186: glo mchin mkhal ma mtsher mkhris pa //
NG0200:4187: gru bzhir gtubs te bzhi bzhi bskor //
NG0200:4188: lag g.yas lho la g.yon pa nub /
NG0200:4189: rkang g.yas shar la g.yon pa byang *//
NG0200:4190: gnas bcu gnas brgyad yongs su rdzogs //
NG0200:4191: las kyi gzhung bsang tshogs 'khor bya //
NG0200:4192: de nas yongs rdzogs lhar bskyed la //
NG0200:4194: lha tshogs sil bu'i mtshan brjod cing *//
NG0200:4195: thugs dam bskang zhing drag tu bskul //
NG0200:4196: don gyi dam rdzas phud dkrol la //
NG0200:4197: dngos grub blang zhing ting 'dzin bsdu //
NG0200:4198: de nas sil bur mchod rdzas bya //
NG0200:4199: sha khrag phud dkrol gtor ma gtang *//
NG0200:4200: rten bsdu rus tshogs sbyin bsreg bya //
NG0200:4201: des ni nyams chag kun bskangs shing *//
NG0200:4203: mtshan ma'i rnam rtog rang sar grol //
NG0200:4204: gsang spyod 'di la rab tu brnan //
NG0200:4206: dpal gsang ba 'dus pa rgyud kyi rgyal po las /
NG0200:4207: dngos grub rdzas chen yongs rdzogs bam sgrub kyi le'u
NG0200:4208: ste nyer gcig pa'o // // de nas yang 'dus
NG0200:4209: pa'i 'khor rnams kyis mgrin gcig tu ston pa kun
NG0200:4210: tu bzang po dpal che mchog he ru ka la
NG0200:4212: 'chi med rdo rje kun tu bzang *//
NG0200:4213: tshe bdag chen po he ru ka / tshe dbang rin chen mchog sgrub thabs //
NG0200:4214: bdag cag rnams la bka' stsol cig / de skad gsol pa'i don dgongs nas //
NG0200:4215: ston pa nyid kyis bka' stsal pa //
NG0200:4216: bla med gsang bsgrub rtse gcig nyon //
NG0200:4217: tshe dbang rin chen mchog sgrub pa //
NG0200:4218: bdud rtsi shel gyi bum bcud bshad //
NG0200:4220: yang sbyor ba dngos rjes te //
NG0200:4221: sngon du bsod nams tshogs chen bsag / dngos gzhi bcud len tshul du'am //
NG0200:4222: rgyas par sgrub chen khog nas dbyung *//
NG0200:4223: de la tshe dbang bcud kyi rdzas //
NG0200:4225: rgyu gnyis rkyen gsum bdud rtsi bzhi //
NG0200:4226: 'di spyad yon tan bsam mi khyab //
NG0200:4227: tshe dbang rdo rje sems dpa' 'grub //
NG0200:4228: de phyir legs sbyar bsgrub na mchog / rgyu gnyis rigs lnga yab yum gyis //
NG0200:4229: byang sems cong zhi brag zhun yin //
NG0200:4230: cong zhi bzang rigs bre gang dang *//
NG0200:4231: brag zhun bzang po phul gang bsog / rkyen gsum rtsi mar srang sum cu //
NG0200:4232: sbrang bre do dang bur bre gsum //
NG0200:4233: bcud bkrag stobs kyis gsos yin bsag / 'chi med bdud rtsi rnam bzhi ni //
NG0200:4234: shug pa ba lu mkhan pa mtshe //
NG0200:4235: 'dab ma me tog bcud bsdus bsag / de rnams sman mar sbyor legs bya //
NG0200:4236: zos na tshe ring nad dkon te //
NG0200:4237: khyad par tshe dbang mchog 'dod na //
NG0200:4238: gsang ba sgrub chen pho brang dbus //
NG0200:4239: lcags bar tsha la med pa ru //
NG0200:4240: sman ril lha grangs mnyam byas blug / par bu'i kha bsdam gzungs thag gdags //
NG0200:4241: dar ser gur phub gu gul bdug / bsnyen sgrub chog khrigs gong bzhin bya //
NG0200:4243: rtsa sngags sham bur 'di nyid bzlas /
NG0200:4244: om badzra sa twa hum b+h+rum a b+h+rum a yur hum ahom badzra sa twa hum /
NG0200:4246: a yur gnya' na hum hri thah /
NG0200:4247: de nas sgrub pa'i sngags 'di bzlas //
NG0200:4251: a mi de wa hrihkarma badzra ha /
NG0200:4252: de nas las sbyor 'chi med sngags //
NG0200:4253: 'di dag bzlas shing dngos grub blang *//
NG0200:4254: om badzra kro d+ha ha ya gri wa hrim /
NG0200:4255: sarba ta tha ga ta ma ha pany+tsa ah /
NG0200:4256: om a yur gnya' na ma ha pun+ya tish+tha om /
NG0200:4257: grub rtags 'od dang du ba sgra /
NG0200:4259: skabs skabs kun tu drang srong rnams //
NG0200:4260: spyan drangs tshe yi gsol ba gdab //
NG0200:4261: de nas rang gzhan dbang bskur ba //
NG0200:4262: bdud rtsi bum pa spyi bor bzhag / rtsa sngags rigs lnga'i snying por bcas //
NG0200:4263: brjod cing rim gyis gnas lngar gtugs //
NG0200:4264: bdud rtsis lus gang rdo rjer bsam //
NG0200:4265: om badzra a yuhshe hum b+h+rum nr-i dzaha b+hi shiny+tsa a /
NG0200:4266: sman phud drang srong lha mchod de //
NG0200:4267: 'ju stobs sbyar zhing rgyun du bza' //
NG0200:4268: zas ngan bsrung zhing 'bru bcud gtang *//
NG0200:4269: mkhas shing man ngag ldan pa gces //
NG0200:4271: sman bcud yon tan bsam mi khyab //
NG0200:4272: rgyu gnyis sman gyis sha rus rgyas //
NG0200:4273: rkyen gsum stobs bcud bkrag kyang 'phel //
NG0200:4274: rtsi bzhi'i tshe ring 'byung ba snyoms //
NG0200:4275: rtsal ni seng chen stobs glang po //
NG0200:4276: mdangs ni rma bya yang rtsal khyung *//
NG0200:4277: gsung ni tshangs pa bang ni rta //
NG0200:4283: bcud len yongs rdzogs 'chi med tshe sgrub kyi le'u
NG0200:4284: ste nyer gnyis pa'o // // de nas yang 'dus
NG0200:4285: pa'i 'khor rnams kyis mgrin gcig tu ston pa kun
NG0200:4286: tu bzang po dpal che mchog he ru ka la
NG0200:4288: skyon gyis ma gos kun tu bzang *//
NG0200:4289: dri med dpal chen he ru ka / dam 'gal nyams pa ji ltar bshags //
NG0200:4290: bdag cag 'khor la bka' stsol cig / de skad gsol pa'i don dgongs nas //
NG0200:4291: ston pa nyid kyis bka' stsal pa //
NG0200:4292: nyams grib gnong 'gyod can nyon cig / sems can las dang rkyen dbang gyis //
NG0200:4293: rtsa ba yan lag nyams srid na //
NG0200:4294: dbang zhu sgo gsum dad bskyed de //
NG0200:4295: bshags thabs rmad byung 'di lta ste //
NG0200:4296: lus ngag yid gsum sgo nas sbyang *//
NG0200:4297: sngags dang phyag rgyas lus nyams bshags //
NG0200:4298: bla ma bde gshegs yongs rdzogs rnams //
NG0200:4299: dbang po'i mngon sum 'dra bar dmigs //
NG0200:4300: na rag dong sprug rkyang phyag 'tshal //
NG0200:4302: phyogs bcu dus bzhi kun gyi bdag nyid che //
NG0200:4303: bla ma zhi khro yongs rdzogs dgongs su gsol //
NG0200:4304: 'dir gshegs nyi zla pad+ma'i gdan la bzhugs //
NG0200:4305: nyams chag na rag sbyang phyir phyag mchod bzhes //
NG0200:4306: yon tan phun tshogs bla ma rnams la phyag 'tshang lo //
NG0200:4307: dmigs med spros bral chos kyi sku la phyag 'tshal lo //
NG0200:4308: bde chen longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku la phyag 'tshal lo //
NG0200:4309: 'gro mgon cir yang sprul pa'i sku la phyag 'tshal lo //
NG0200:4310: gnas lugs mi 'gyur rdo rje'i sku la phyag 'tshal lo //
NG0200:4311: yang dag mngon par byang chub sku la phyag 'tshal lo //
NG0200:4312: nyon mongs 'joms mdzad zhi ba'i lha la phyag 'tshal lo //
NG0200:4313: log lta tshar gcod khro bo'i lha la phyag 'tshal lo //
NG0200:4314: thabs mgon tshe bdag 'jam dpal sku la phyag 'tshal lo //
NG0200:4315: skyon bral sgra sgrogs pad+ma'i gsung la phyag 'tshal lo //
NG0200:4316: yang dag don ldan badzra thugs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NG0200:4317: dug lnga'i nad sel bdud rtsi sman la phyag 'tshal lo //
NG0200:4318: dregs pa 'joms mdzad phur pa'i lha la phyag 'tshal lo //
NG0200:4319: 'byung ba'i mnga' bdag ma mo'i tshogs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NG0200:4320: sa dang lam rdzogs rig 'dzin tshogs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NG0200:4321: bstan pa bsrung mdzad dam can tshogs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NG0200:4322: dgra bgegs bdud 'dul sngags bdag rnams la phyag 'tshal lo //
NG0200:4323: de rjes phyag rgya'i lha mchog bsgom //
NG0200:4324: gang gis rgyal ba zhi khro yi //
NG0200:4325: dkyil 'khor mtshan thos phyag btsal na //
NG0200:4326: nyams chag ma lus kun byang na //
NG0200:4327: mtshams med lnga la smos ci dgos //
NG0200:4328: na rag gnas kyang dong sprugs te //
NG0200:4329: rig 'dzin rgyal ba'i zhing du grags //
NG0200:4330: sngags bzlas skyon mthol ngag nyams bshags //
NG0200:4331: rdo rje sems dpa' gtsug tu dmigs //
NG0200:4332: las sgrib nyams grib dag byed pa //
NG0200:4333: 'khor ba dong sprug yang snying 'di dag bzlas //
NG0200:4336: om badzra sa twa sa ma ya /
NG0200:4338: badzra sa twa twe no pa tish+tha dr-i d+ho me b+ha wa /
NG0200:4339: su to sh+yo me b+ha wa /
NG0200:4340: a nu rak+to me b+ha wa /
NG0200:4341: su po sh+yo me b+ha wa /
NG0200:4344: tsit+tam shwi yam ku ru hum /
NG0200:4352: de brjod rgyal ba'i sras su 'gyur //
NG0200:4353: ho bde gshegs yongs rdzogs dgongs su gsol //
NG0200:4354: rgyal ba'i bka' dang bla ma'i lung *//
NG0200:4355: ji bzhin ma spyad slob dpon smad //
NG0200:4356: rdo rje mched dang lcam dral la //
NG0200:4357: lta log ngan sems ngan du smras //
NG0200:4358: brdeg btsog gnod pa dngos su spyad //
NG0200:4359: lha dang dkyil 'khor nyams ma gsal //
NG0200:4360: 'dzab bzlas ma dag zur chag g.yel //
NG0200:4361: gsang bar 'os dang gnyer gtad smras //
NG0200:4362: gsang bcu bsgrags dang bla ma bslus //
NG0200:4363: rtsa ba'i dam nyams mthol zhing bshags //
NG0200:4364: gzhan yang spyad bya'i dam tshig lnga //
NG0200:4365: mi spang lnga dang dang len lnga //
NG0200:4366: shes bya lnga dang bsgrub bya lnga //
NG0200:4367: yan lag dam nyams mthol zhing bshags //
NG0200:4368: bsnyen bsgrub ting 'dzin dam g.yel zhing *//
NG0200:4369: nya bzhi dus drug dus mchod chag / le lo gsog 'jog tshogs sbyang byas //
NG0200:4370: phud lhag nyams shing kha tshar shor //
NG0200:4371: tshor dang ma tshor rkyen dbang gis //
NG0200:4372: sgo gsum bag med dam nyams bshags //
NG0200:4373: yid kyi dam nyams lta bas bshags //
NG0200:4374: de yang kun gzhi byang chub sems //
NG0200:4375: yin pa med pa'i lta bas rtogs //
NG0200:4376: min pa med pa'i sgom nyams lon //
NG0200:4377: yin min med pa'i spyod pas rtogs //
NG0200:4378: re dogs med pa'i byang chub ni //
NG0200:4379: rtsa ba yan lag thams cad kyi //
NG0200:4380: chag nyams ma byung ma skyes pas //
NG0200:4381: bshag bya bshags byed gnyis med grol //
NG0200:4383: dpal gsang ba 'dus pa brgyud kyi rgyal po las /
NG0200:4384: 'gyod tshangs yongs rdzogs na rag dong sprug / bshags
NG0200:4385: pa'i le'u ste nyer gsum pa'o // // de nas
NG0200:4386: yang 'dus pa'i 'khor rnams kyis mgrin gcig tu ston
NG0200:4387: pa kun tu bzang po dpal che mchog he ru
NG0200:4391: thams cad tshigs byed nam mkha'i mdzod //
NG0200:4392: lha rnams mdangs kyis ji ltar bskang *//
NG0200:4393: bdag cag 'khor la bka' stsol cig / de skad gsol pa'i don dgongs nas //
NG0200:4394: ston pa nyid kyis bka' stsal pa //
NG0200:4396: rtsa lag dam tshig g.yel nyams nyon //
NG0200:4397: le los dus mchod chag pa'am //
NG0200:4398: lha dang 'khon gcugs sbyang ba dang *//
NG0200:4399: bsod nams tshogs chen bsag bya'i phyir //
NG0200:4400: bskang gso'i rim pa 'di lta ste //
NG0200:4401: dkyil 'khor gzhung bzhin bzhengs pa'i rtsar //
NG0200:4402: lha bkram rten gyi tshogs kyang bsham //
NG0200:4403: 'byor ldan yo byad gtor mchod bsham //
NG0200:4404: skal ldan mi yi tshogs kyang bsham //
NG0200:4407: dang po lta dgongs bshags pa bya //
NG0200:4408: de 'og mchod rdzas rang rtags brjod //
NG0200:4409: bla ma lha tshogs mtshan brjod de //
NG0200:4410: mdangs bskang cho ga rgyas par bya //
NG0200:4411: de nas phur gdab sbyor sgrol bskang *//
NG0200:4412: rjes su rkyen bzlog byol chen gdab //
NG0200:4413: de rnams rdzas kyi phyi skong yin //
NG0200:4414: dam can kun mnyes rkyen dbang bzlog / nang ni ting nge 'dzin gyis bskang *//
NG0200:4416: snod kyi 'jig rten gzhong pa ru //
NG0200:4417: bcud kyi sems can 'dod yon spung *//
NG0200:4418: rig pa'i lha mo spros te bskang *//
NG0200:4419: gzugs spyan sgra snyan dri shangs dang *//
NG0200:4420: ro mchog ljags la reg bya sku //
NG0200:4421: snang srid bcud kyis thugs dam bskang *//
NG0200:4422: 'dod yon dbang po lngar thim nas //
NG0200:4423: lha mnyes phrin las bsgrub par bsam //
NG0200:4424: des ni lha mnyes dngos grub ster //
NG0200:4425: gsang ba gnyis med lta bas bskang *//
NG0200:4426: bskang bya'i lha sems skong byed kyi //
NG0200:4427: mkhan po dag kyang rang gi sems //
NG0200:4428: skong ba'i rdzas mchog sems yin pas //
NG0200:4429: sems nyid gzhi rtsa bral ba la //
NG0200:4430: mchod bya mchod byed gnyis med pas //
NG0200:4431: gnyis med don gyi thugs dam bskang *//
NG0200:4432: ye shes lha tshogs kun mnyes nas //
NG0200:4433: mchog gi dngos grub rgyun mi 'chad //
NG0200:4435: dpal gsang ba 'dus pa rgyud kyi rgyal po las
NG0200:4436: // thugs dam yongs su bskang ba'i le'u ste nyer
NG0200:4437: bzhi pa'o // // de nas yang 'dus pa'i 'khor
NG0200:4438: rnams kyis mgrin gcig tu ston pa kun tu bzang
NG0200:4439: po dpal che mchog he ru ka la gsol pa
NG0200:4441: 'jig rten dbang phyug kun tu bzang *//
NG0200:4442: 'khor 'das mdos bdag he ru ka / lha 'khrugs mdos kyis ji ltar bskang *//
NG0200:4443: bdag cag 'khor la bka' stsol cig / de skad gsol pa'i don dgongs te //
NG0200:4444: ston pa chen pos bka' stsal pa //
NG0200:4445: 'gro phan byams sems can rnams nyon //
NG0200:4447: de dag mdos kyis bsal phyir dang *//
NG0200:4448: nyams chag gso dang mtshon 'khrug gcod //
NG0200:4449: nad gdon gnod pa zhi byed cing *//
NG0200:4450: tshe dang longs spyod bsod nams spel //
NG0200:4451: snang srid dbang sdud dgra bgegs sgrol //
NG0200:4452: don chen kun sgrub phur kha bzlog / rtog tshogs lha ru ngo sprad cing *//
NG0200:4454: yongs rdzogs gling bzhi spyi mdos bshad //
NG0200:4455: rnam dag spros bral chos sku las //
NG0200:4456: byin rlabs longs sku dpe byad ldan //
NG0200:4457: thugs rje'i sprul sku bsam yas kyang *//
NG0200:4458: bsdu na bka' brgyad yongs rdzogs yin //
NG0200:4459: las dang ye shes tshul du snang *//
NG0200:4460: lta spyod zung 'jug mdos kyis bskang *//
NG0200:4461: de la ngo bo nges tshig dang *//
NG0200:4462: dbye ba mthun dpe dgos ched dang *//
NG0200:4463: bsham thabs sngon 'gro dngos rjes kyis //
NG0200:4464: nyams blangs thag bcad 'bras bu bstan //
NG0200:4465: ngo bo gnyis med byang chub sems //
NG0200:4468: dbye na las dang ye shes kyis //
NG0200:4469: bsdus te pho mdos mo mdos dang *//
NG0200:4470: yongs rdzogs spyi mdos rnam gsum ste //
NG0200:4471: phyi nang gsang ba'i mdos su bstan //
NG0200:4473: dgos ched mchog dang thun mong dang *//
NG0200:4474: gnyis med bde chen don rtogs shing *//
NG0200:4475: phrin las bzhi sogs las kun grub //
NG0200:4476: bsham thabs mdos dngos mchod rdzas rgyan //
NG0200:4477: sa stegs 'dom gang gru bzhi pa'i /
NG0200:4479: rat+na brdar te gong bu bcos //
NG0200:4480: hum ram yam kham lam b+h+rum /
NG0200:4482: ri rab gling bzhi bzang por bsham //
NG0200:4483: steng du pho brang gling dgu la //
NG0200:4484: ye shes lha rnams dbang rdzas ni //
NG0200:4485: snying phye'i dpal bshos rtse dgu la //
NG0200:4486: sngags ldan phur nag dgu yang gzug / dbus su dpal chen dgu po la //
NG0200:4487: zhal mthun kun tu zhal dgu gzug / spyi gdugs chen po gcig 'og tu //
NG0200:4488: gdugs brgyad 'phan dang rgyal mtshan gzug / mda' dgu rang rtags phyag mtshan bri //
NG0200:4489: shing ris zhal dgu 'phan dgu dang *//
NG0200:4490: dar rgyang ru mtshon pho mo'i gdong *//
NG0200:4491: dar glud pho glud mo glud dgu / 'khor los sgyur ba lta bur dgram //
NG0200:4492: bang rim gsum pa yan chod du //
NG0200:4493: yongs rdzogs spyi skong dam rdzas su //
NG0200:4494: nam mkha' dbus mthing mtha' 'ja' ris //
NG0200:4495: khri gzhad rma bya dar snas brgyan //
NG0200:4496: stag gzig gung gi rgyal mtshan dang *//
NG0200:4497: ru mtshon dar rgyang mda' 'phang dang *//
NG0200:4498: shing ris dar 'phan la sogs te //
NG0200:4499: stong dang lnga brgya brgya la sogs //
NG0200:4500: rab 'bring tha ma gang spobs bsag / khyung chen
NG0200:4501: rma bya seng ge 'brug / stag gzig glang chen
NG0200:4502: rta mchog dang *// skyes pa bud med glud la sogs //
NG0200:4503: re re'ang stong sogs ci rigs bsham //
NG0200:4504: bang rim tha mar sde brgyad rdzas //
NG0200:4505: nam mkha' mda' 'phang rgyal mtshan dang */
NG0200:4506: gzugs glud la sogs so so dang *//
NG0200:4507: mthun par ci rigs skye 'gro bsag / gling bzhi las kyi pho nya ste //
NG0200:4508: srid pa'i dbang chen sde bzhi la //
NG0200:4509: nam mkha' mda' 'phang rgyal mtshan sogs //
NG0200:4510: gzugs glud dam rdzas tshang bar bsham //
NG0200:4511: gzhan yang ri rab gling khengs par //
NG0200:4513: mar me gser skyems rin chen dang *//
NG0200:4514: sna tshogs dar gyis bklubs la bzhag / zor rdzas kun gyis mtha' ma bskor //
NG0200:4515: phyi yi lha tshogs mnyes mdos yin //
NG0200:4516: sgyu lus phung po'i ri rab la //
NG0200:4517: rnam rtog phra rags rdzas kyis brgyan //
NG0200:4518: nang gi lha tshogs skong mdos yin //
NG0200:4519: b+ha ga'i gzhi la gsang ri rab //
NG0200:4520: byang chub sems sprin rgyan gyis brgyan //
NG0200:4521: bde mchog don ldan chos skur rdzogs //
NG0200:4522: gsang ba'i lha tshogs mchod mdos yin //
NG0200:4523: de ltar phun sum tshogs bshams nas //
NG0200:4524: mdos kyi sngon du 'gro ba ni //
NG0200:4525: phud gtang tsha chu mdo yang bklag / las kyi gzhung bsrang 'dzab bzlas bya //
NG0200:4528: che mchog dgu bstod nga rgyal bya //
NG0200:4529: snang srid mdos su byin gyis brlab //
NG0200:4530: mdos kyi mtshon pa la brten nas //
NG0200:4531: las kyi lha rnams rdzas kyis bskang *//
NG0200:4532: ye shes lha rnams don gyis bskang *//
NG0200:4533: gnyis su med par thugs dam bskang *//
NG0200:4534: yongs rdzogs rjes su bye brag bsngo //
NG0200:4535: phrin las rnam bzhi la sogs pa'i //
NG0200:4536: gang bsgrub las gnyer so sor gtad //
NG0200:4537: zor bsgyur sgo dbye lam bstan bya //
NG0200:4538: tshe 'gugs bkra shis cho ga bya //
NG0200:4539: dbyings nas mdos phyung 'gro don mdzad //
NG0200:4540: slar yang chos kyi dbyings su thim //
NG0200:4541: dngos grub thams cad mdo las 'byung *//
NG0200:4543: dpal gsang ba 'dus pa rgyud kyi rgyal po las /
NG0200:4544: yongs rdzogs gling bzhi srid pa spyi mdos kyi le'u
NG0200:4545: ste nyer lnga pa'o // // de nas yang 'dus
NG0200:4546: pa'i 'khor rnams kyis mgrin gcig tu ston pa kun
NG0200:4547: tu bzang po dpal che mchog he ru ka la
NG0200:4549: thams cad ston pa kun tu bzang *//
NG0200:4550: thugs rje che mchog he ru ka / ji srid bar du 'gro 'dul ba'i //
NG0200:4551: sku gsung thugs rten bzheng thabs gang *//
NG0200:4552: zhes gsol ston pas bka' stsal pa //
NG0200:4553: bde gshegs sku gsung thugs yongs rdzogs //
NG0200:4554: snod bcud tshul du bzheng thabs bshad //
NG0200:4555: dang po snod kyi gzhal yas khang *//
NG0200:4556: yid 'ong dge zhing dul ba'i sar //
NG0200:4557: sa yi sta gon sngon song nas //
NG0200:4558: snod kyi 'jig rten rtog sbyang phyir //
NG0200:4559: ri rab gling bcas cha mthun du //
NG0200:4560: brtsigs te chos sgo bsam yas par //
NG0200:4561: gzhal yas sgo mang chen por bzhengs //
NG0200:4562: sku gsum yongs su rdzogs bya'i phyir //
NG0200:4563: mnyam nyid chos skur byin brlabs te //
NG0200:4564: sa gzhi cha mnyam stong par sbyang *//
NG0200:4565: ma 'gags longs skur byin brlab phyir //
NG0200:4566: yongs rdzogs dkyil 'khor bzhengs la gdul //
NG0200:4567: thugs rje sprul skur byin brlab phyir //
NG0200:4568: pan rag brtsig par bya ba ni //
NG0200:4569: pan rag steng nas rmang bres te //
NG0200:4570: grub thob dge gnas sa sna dang *//
NG0200:4571: dpal che re bzang gangs rdo dang *//
NG0200:4572: lung bzang mdo dgu'i bye smyag dang *//
NG0200:4573: rat+na lnga yi phye mar sbyar //
NG0200:4574: 'dam shig sngon song rgyu sbyangs te //
NG0200:4575: gzhal yas phyi dbyibs mngon sum mthun //
NG0200:4576: lha rnams theg pa yongs rdzogs dgod //
NG0200:4577: de bzhin bzheng thabs rim pa yang *//
NG0200:4578: 'byung ba lnga brtseg cha mthun par //
NG0200:4579: gdan ni rim pa lnga brtseg steng *//
NG0200:4580: ri rab ri bo mchog bzhin du //
NG0200:4581: gzhal yas bang rim bzhi ldan la //
NG0200:4582: khong seng khri rkang cha mthun du //
NG0200:4583: sgo mo dgu bcu go gsum dgod //
NG0200:4584: rnam rgyal khang bzang cha mthun du //
NG0200:4585: pho brang gru bzhi bskor byas brtsig / lha dbang gtso khang cha mthun du //
NG0200:4586: bre bzang sgo bzhi ldan par brtsig / yongs 'du+u sa brtol cha mthun par //
NG0200:4587: srog shing bzang po ma thung gzug / sum cu rtsa gsum cha mthun par //
NG0200:4590: min cha mthun char khebs tog / bya ru la sogs mdzes par dgod //
NG0200:4591: lcog mtshon grwa bzhir grwa lcog bya //
NG0200:4592: ri bdun mtshon phyir 'khor yug tu //
NG0200:4593: 'khor sa bang rim bdun gyis bskor //
NG0200:4594: nyi zla'i tshul du sgrol ma dang *//
NG0200:4595: spyan ras gzigs khang shar nub brgyan //
NG0200:4596: mtsho bdun rgya mtsho mtshon pa'i phyir //
NG0200:4597: g.yu thang legs bya khron bu bru //
NG0200:4598: gling bzhi'i gling phran tshul mthun du //
NG0200:4599: sa steng gling gzugs bcu gnyis te //
NG0200:4600: sprul sku'i mchod rten bcu gnyis btsig / mu khyud cha mthun brag ris bskor //
NG0200:4601: de la tshad med sgo bzhi dgod //
NG0200:4602: rten gnas che chung spobs par sbyar //
NG0200:4603: de ltar rten gnas de nyid la //
NG0200:4604: brten pa bcud kyi 'jig rten dag / sbyang phyir lha tshogs bzheng thabs bshad //
NG0200:4605: stod rim gsum ni sku gsum zhing *//
NG0200:4606: nyan thos rang rgyal byang sems kyi //
NG0200:4607: gzugs rnams rgyas bsdus ci rigs par //
NG0200:4608: bang rim 'og ma'i sgo nang bkod //
NG0200:4609: de ltar bang rim gsum sgo'i nang *//
NG0200:4610: kri ya u pa yo ga yi //
NG0200:4611: lha rnams rgyas bsdus gang 'tshams dgod //
NG0200:4612: bre bum bdag por gdugs tog nang *//
NG0200:4613: ma ha a nu a ti yi //
NG0200:4614: lha rnams yongs rdzogs zhi dang khro //
NG0200:4615: bka' brgyad bsgrub pa'i lha dgod de //
NG0200:4616: kun bzang tog la bzang mo gdugs //
NG0200:4617: 'khor lo rdor sems 'degs gsang bdag / bre stod zhi lha bzhi bcu gnyis //
NG0200:4618: bre smad nang sgo bcu gnyis gzug / khrag 'thung lnga bcu rtsa brgyad dgod //
NG0200:4619: bum dkyil bum pa'i phyogs mtshams su //
NG0200:4620: bka' brgyad yongs rdzogs lha rnams dgod //
NG0200:4621: sgo bzhi rgyal chen sde bzhi la //
NG0200:4622: gza' brgyad rgyu skar bskor ba dgod //
NG0200:4623: lcog bzhi gnod sbyin nor gyi lha //
NG0200:4624: pho dgu mo dgu la sogs dgod //
NG0200:4625: gdan rim lnga brtsegs steng nang du //
NG0200:4626: klu dbang nyi nyid la yang zla brgyad bskor bzhengs //
NG0200:4627: de 'og gru gsum dong nang du //
NG0200:4628: sangs rgyas bstan pa'i dgra bgegs grub //
NG0200:4629: 'khor sa rim pa bdun nang du //
NG0200:4630: bskal bzang sangs rgyas stor rtsa gnyis //
NG0200:4631: mdo 'dul chos mngon rgyud ris bris //
NG0200:4632: nyi ma'i khang par thugs rje che //
NG0200:4633: zla khang sgrol ma myur ma dgod //
NG0200:4634: gling bzhi gling phran brgyad steng du //
NG0200:4635: mchod rten chen po bcu gnyis nang *//
NG0200:4636: sprul sku'i mdzad pa bcu gnyis dgod //
NG0200:4637: 'khor yug re re rwa ba'i nang */
NG0200:4638: bstan pa srung ba'i lha ma srin //
NG0200:4639: chos skyong pho nya'i tshogs rnams dgod //
NG0200:4640: sgo bzhir dbang chen sde bzhi dang *//
NG0200:4641: ha ri ka dang pany+tsi ka / kang king lha
NG0200:4642: mo mgon po nag / sgrol ging dkar dang nag
NG0200:4643: po dgod // lha tshogs de dag thams cad kyang *//
NG0200:4644: lugs 'bur ri mor gang lcogs bzhengs //
NG0200:4645: sngags dang phyag rgyas smin par bya //
NG0200:4646: spyi gtsug gdung gzhug mgrin pa ru //
NG0200:4647: a li ka li gzhug par bya //
NG0200:4648: thugs kar man shel hum bcas gzhug / srog shing rtse nas rmang yan chod //
NG0200:4649: theg pa'i rim pa dang sbyar ba'i //
NG0200:4651: man ngag rim par gzhug / srog shing nang du srog phur gdab //
NG0200:4652: srog shing phyi la tshe dpag med //
NG0200:4653: gzugs dang sngags su bcas pa dgod //
NG0200:4654: kha dog phyogs mtshon gdul byar bstan //
NG0200:4655: dar bzang la sogs na bzas bklub //
NG0200:4656: bang rim dang po nas brtsams te //
NG0200:4657: bsgrub rdzas mchod rdzas rkyen dbang bzlog / bang rim
NG0200:4658: gsum pa'i nang du bsag / bum dkyil bsgrub khang
NG0200:4659: rnal 'byor gnas // sgo rnams la ni 'khor rim bzhin //
NG0200:4660: nyams len bsgrub pa'i gnas byas na //
NG0200:4661: grub pa mthar phyin 'khrul pa sel //
NG0200:4662: sku gsum rgyal ba zhi dang khro //
NG0200:4663: gsang ba yongs rdzogs bde gshegs kyi //
NG0200:4664: rten gsum yongs rdzogs ngo mtshar che //
NG0200:4665: rten 'di ji srid gnas kyi bar //
NG0200:4666: de srid sangs rgyas bstan pa rgyas //
NG0200:4668: bsod nams phun tshogs yongs rdzogs shing *//
NG0200:4669: rgyu sbyor bzhengs mkhan ma lus kun //
NG0200:4671: phyi ma zhing khams rnam dag thob //
NG0200:4672: yul phyogs gling khams bkra shis 'byung *//
NG0200:4673: thabs mchog yongs rdzogs rmad du byung *//
NG0200:4674: bstan pa'i rim gro 'di kho na //
NG0200:4675: dang du longs shig bsam pa 'grub //
NG0200:4677: dpal gsang ba 'dus pa rgyud kyi rgyal po las /
NG0200:4678: rten mchog bkra shis sku gsum yongs rdzogs su bzhengs
NG0200:4679: thabs bstan pa'i le'u ste nyer drug pa'o //// de
NG0200:4680: nas yang 'dus pa'i 'khor rnams kyis mgrin gcig tu
NG0200:4681: ston pa kun tu bzang po dpal che mchog he
NG0200:4684: thams cad ston pa kun tu bzang *//
NG0200:4685: thugs rje che mchog he ru ka / bde gshegs sku gsung thugs rten la //
NG0200:4686: ye shes rab tu gnas thabs gang *//
NG0200:4687: zhes gsol ston pas bka' stsal pa //
NG0200:4688: bde gshegs sku gsung yongs rdzogs rten //
NG0200:4689: rab tu gnas thabs rnam gsum bshad //
NG0200:4690: spros pa rgyas bsdus spros med de //
NG0200:4691: rgyas mdzad bla ma mkhas pa la //
NG0200:4692: slob bus yon dbul lan gsum bar //
NG0200:4693: gsol ba gdab cing bla mas kyang *//
NG0200:4694: rtags sbyar rab gnas bsnyen pa bya //
NG0200:4695: dus tshod gza' skar bzang po la //
NG0200:4696: gsang ba sgrub chen skabs bzhin du //
NG0200:4697: dkyil 'khor rten rdzas sngon song nas //
NG0200:4698: dkyil 'khor de yi byang phyogs su //
NG0200:4699: rten gsum gang yin khri la bzhag / brab bdug bgegs bskrad srung 'khor bsgom //
NG0200:4700: skyabs 'gro sems bskyed mchod sbyin bya //
NG0200:4701: gsol ba gdab cing bsnyen pa bskyal //
NG0200:4702: tshul bzhin bsgrubs te byin chen dbab //
NG0200:4704: sngags kyis bgegs bskrad chal gyis bkru //
NG0200:4705: ras sam dar gyis rdul phyis la //
NG0200:4706: ram yam kham gyis rab tu sbyang *//
NG0200:4707: tsan dan gur gum a ga ru //
NG0200:4708: dza ti gla rtsi dri lngas byug / sku dang mchod rten gang yin yang *//
NG0200:4709: sku gsung thugs dang rten 'brel snying *//
NG0200:4710: bde gshegs yongs rdzogs yang snying @#//
NG0200:4712: rigs dbye sku yi gnas lngar gzhug / sku gdung ring bsrel nor bu lnga //
NG0200:4713: sman 'bru dar gyis bril te gzhug / de nas dkyil 'khor legs bris te //
NG0200:4714: bum pa la sogs mchod rdzas bsham //
NG0200:4715: bskyed rdzogs las kyi gzhung bsrangs nas //
NG0200:4716: mchod bstod bzlas pa tshul bzhin bya //
NG0200:4717: bum pa byin brlab bzhu btul bya //
NG0200:4718: rten la bgegs bskrad sku khrus bya //
NG0200:4719: rten spyir bskyed rdzogs sngar bzhin bya //
NG0200:4720: sku gsung thugs su byin brlabs la //
NG0200:4721: ye shes lnga yi dbang yang bskur //
NG0200:4722: spyan 'byed snyan shangs zhal tshems drud //
NG0200:4723: longs sku'i rten la na bza' gsol //
NG0200:4724: dbu rgyan cod pan phreng ba gdags //
NG0200:4725: sprul sku yin na dbu skra bzhar //
NG0200:4726: glegs bam dag la bde gshegs yongs //
NG0200:4727: gsal dbyangs lnga bcu'i yi ge bsgyur //
NG0200:4729: mchod rten dkyil 'khor cha mthun par //
NG0200:4730: nang du tshom dgu'i lha tshogs bskyed //
NG0200:4731: de la ye shes dkyil 'khor dgug / bstim brtan dgyes pa bskyed pa dang *//
NG0200:4732: phyag sogs mchod pa kun gyis mchod //
NG0200:4733: gdugs dang rgyal mtshan bla bre sogs //
NG0200:4734: rnam bdun bkra shis rdzas brgyad dbul //
NG0200:4736: rten gsum rim pa gang yin yang *//
NG0200:4737: ye shes yang yang dgu cing bstim //
NG0200:4738: sngags kyi bzlas pa so sor bya //
NG0200:4739: sku+u gsung thugs su byin brlab cing *//
NG0200:4740: ye shes lnga yi dbang bskur bya //
NG0200:4741: bum dbang gzhung bzhin bskur ba'i rjes //
NG0200:4742: nas 'bru me tog dkar po la //
NG0200:4744: na mo rat+na tra ya ya /
NG0200:4745: om ye d+harma he tu pra b+ha wa he tun+te shan+ta tha ga to h+ya wa data /
NG0200:4746: te shany+tsa yo ni ro d+ha e wam ba di ma ha shra ma nahswa ha /
NG0200:4747: de rjes bu slob yon bdag la //
NG0200:4748: bum dbang bkra shis rdzas bzhi dang *//
NG0200:4749: sna bdun rdzas brgyad dbang bskur bya //
NG0200:4750: tshogs 'khor bzang pos zhal bsro bya //
NG0200:4751: kha brda bzang smra spyod lam gzab //
NG0200:4752: bkra shis skyid pa'i lha bro bya //
NG0200:4753: rgyas pa'i sbyin bsreg smon lam gdab //
NG0200:4754: phud gtor lha dang chos skyong mchod //
NG0200:4755: rten gyi gnyer gtad drag tu bya //
NG0200:4756: gtang rag mchod pa dga' ston bya //
NG0200:4757: yon dbul dge ba'i rtsa ba bsngo //
NG0200:4758: spros pa nyer bsdu'i rab gnas ni //
NG0200:4759: sngon 'gro khrus sogs yongs rdzogs rjes //
NG0200:4760: gang la bya ba'i rten de nyid //
NG0200:4761: cho ga gsum gyis sbyangs byas te //
NG0200:4762: rang rang ye shes ngo bor bsam //
NG0200:4763: de la dbang bskur me tog gtor //
NG0200:4764: mchod pa bzang po mang phul nas //
NG0200:4765: yi dam lhag pa'i rten du bzung *//
NG0200:4766: ji ltar bsam pa de bzhin yin //
NG0200:4767: spros med don gyi rab gnas ni //
NG0200:4768: bsnyen rdzogs rtogs ldan rnal 'byor pas //
NG0200:4769: gzigs pas rab tu gnas pa 'chags //
NG0200:4770: phyi nang snod bcud snang srid kun //
NG0200:4771: ye nas chos sku'i ngo bor gnas //
NG0200:4772: der shes dbyings las ma g.yos na //
NG0200:4773: rnam dag rten mchog bla na med //
NG0200:4776: (6)@#// ba sku la grag pa gsung *//
NG0200:4777: dran rtog thugs kyi rang bzhin yin //
NG0200:4778: sku gsung thugs rten yongs rdzogs kyang *//
NG0200:4779: blo dman blo la der mi snang *//
NG0200:4780: shes rab blo ldan skyes mchog gis //
NG0200:4781: rdul gcig steng na rdul snyed kyi //
NG0200:4782: sangs rgyas ma lus yongs rdzogs skur //
NG0200:4783: rab gnas dam pa de nyid do //
NG0200:4784: rang rig rang gsal rab gnas rab //
NG0200:4785: rab gnas kun gyi rgyal po yin //
NG0200:4786: rab gnas phun tshogs de dag gis //
NG0200:4787: ji srid yun gyi rten byas na //
NG0200:4788: bkra shis byin chen bsam legs 'grub //
NG0200:4789: 'bras bu sku gsum zhing du sbyor //
NG0200:4791: dpal gsang ba 'dus pa'i rgyud kyi rgyal po las /
NG0200:4792: rten gsum rab gnas yongs rdzogs kyi le'u ste nyer
NG0200:4793: bdun pa'o // // de nas yang 'dus pa'i 'khor
NG0200:4794: rnams kyis mgrin gcig tu ston pa kun tu bzang
NG0200:4795: po dpal che mchog he ru ka la gsol pa
NG0200:4797: thams cad ston pa kun tu bzang *//
NG0200:4798: thugs rje che mchog he ru ka / sgo gsum bar chad kun skyob pa'i //
NG0200:4800: bdag cag 'khor la bka' stsol cig / de skad gsol pa'i don dgongs nas //
NG0200:4801: ston pa chen pos bka' stsal pa //
NG0200:4802: bde gshegs bka' yi srung 'khor la //
NG0200:4804: kun thub 'khor lo'i srung ba la //
NG0200:4805: shog shog ras sam dar dkar la //
NG0200:4806: rat+na lnga sbyar snag tsha yis //
NG0200:4807: dbus su thig bzhi ling tshe dgu / re re'i nang du 'khor lo ni //
NG0200:4808: rtsibs brgyad khyud 'khor bzhi ldan bri //
NG0200:4809: de dgu'i gong ras dgu po la //
NG0200:4810: rigs kyi phyag mtshan gtams par bya //
NG0200:4811: ling dgu'i phyi rol mu khyud ni //
NG0200:4812: rim pa bcu ru bskor bar bya //
NG0200:4813: de la sngags dgod rim pa ni //
NG0200:4814: dbus 'khor dgu yi lte ba la //
NG0200:4815: hum dgu ming rus rak+shar bcas //
NG0200:4816: srungs shig 'dod gsol dang bcas bri //
NG0200:4817: de'i phyi lte ba'i khyud dgu la //
NG0200:4818: khro 'dus drag sngags so lnga bri //
NG0200:4819: rtsibs brgyad 'khor lo dgu rnams su //
NG0200:4820: dpal chen dgu yi skyed sngags bri //
NG0200:4821: mu khyud phyi ru sras yum dang *//
NG0200:4822: bo d+hi bcu bzhi khyung sngags drug / dam can 'dus pa bcu gcig bri //
NG0200:4823: rtsibs mchan khyab par srungs shig bri //
NG0200:4824: gong ras khyab par gsang sngags dang *//
NG0200:4825: rig sngags gzungs sngags stobs can dgod //
NG0200:4826: gling bzhi'i phyi rol zla gam bzhi //
NG0200:4827: rgyal chen bzhi yi ru pas bsrung *//
NG0200:4828: mu khyud bcu rim nang ma che //
NG0200:4829: de la zhi khro bka' brgyad rdzogs //
NG0200:4830: bde gshegs kun gyi yang snying la //
NG0200:4831: che ge la srungs spel mar bri //
NG0200:4832: de yi phyi rim dbyangs yig la //
NG0200:4833: de'i phyi gsal byed rten 'brel bri //
NG0200:4834: phyi rim mu khyud bdun pa la //
NG0200:4835: rdo rje 'khor lo ral gri dang *//
NG0200:4836: dbyug to rgya gram mtshon cha'i tshogs //
NG0200:4837: me ri lnga yis 'khor bar bri //
NG0200:4838: rdzas kyi bsrung ba'i skyobs ngar gdags //
NG0200:4839: ga bur tsan dan gla rtsi dang *//
NG0200:4840: gu gur gum yang gul li shi shing kun @#//
NG0200:4842: a mr-i ta dang chang sbyar byug / gtor tshogs gzhung bzhin bshams nas kyang *//
NG0200:4843: las rim gzhung bsrang lha rnams bstim //
NG0200:4844: dbang bskur rab tu gnas pa bya //
NG0200:4845: dar sna lngas dril tshon lngas bcings //
NG0200:4846: dus tshes bzang la mgul du gdags //
NG0200:4847: bkra shis mnga' gsol brjod par bya //
NG0200:4848: ting 'dzin rang nyid he ru ka / yongs su rdzogs pa'i nga rgyal bsgom //
NG0200:4852: ci phyir 'di nyid yongs rdzogs yin //
NG0200:4853: lus ngag yid gsum srung ba'i mkhar //
NG0200:4854: rdo rje'i go khrab phub chen yin //
NG0200:4855: nad gdon dug mtshon gnam lcags bsrung *//
NG0200:4856: mdor na 'jigs pa kun thub ste //
NG0200:4857: phyogs ngan kun dang gnod las rgyal //
NG0200:4858: tshe 'di bar do phyi ma yi //
NG0200:4860: ngan song gnas ngan kun las grol //
NG0200:4862: rgyal ba rnams kyi sras su gzigs //
NG0200:4863: dam can rnams kyis mgon stongs mdzad //
NG0200:4864: lha srin sde brgyad bran du 'khol //
NG0200:4865: 'da' khar byang chub rtags la sbyor //
NG0200:4867: dpal gsang ba 'dus pa rgyud kyi rgyal po las /
NG0200:4868: bde gshegs yongs rdzogs bka'i srung 'khor bstan pa'i le'u
NG0200:4869: ste nyer brgyad pa'o // // de nas yang 'dus
NG0200:4870: pa'i 'khor rnams kyis mgrin gcig tu ston pa kun
NG0200:4871: tu bzang po dpal che mchog he ru ka la
NG0200:4873: thams cad ston pa kun tu bzang *//
NG0200:4874: thugs rje che mchog he ru ka / sgrub chen las bzhi'i don myur byed //
NG0200:4875: sbyin bsreg las kyi rim pa gang *//
NG0200:4876: de skad gsol pa gsan nas kyang *//
NG0200:4877: ston pa nyid kyis bka' stsal pa //
NG0200:4878: las rnams kun gyi rjes sgrub myur //
NG0200:4879: rnam bzhi sbyin bsreg 'di ltar bya //
NG0200:4880: dkyil 'khor chen po'i phyogs bzhi ru //
NG0200:4881: zhi rgyas dbang dang drag po'i thab //
NG0200:4882: zlum po gru bzhi zla kham dang *//
NG0200:4883: gru gsum la sogs gang mos bya //
NG0200:4884: dkar ser dmar ljang kha dog bsgyur //
NG0200:4885: byang chub skyer ldeng dug shing sogs //
NG0200:4886: las mthun shing brtsig bsreg pa'i rdzas //
NG0200:4887: phrin las gang bsgrub dang sbyar te //
NG0200:4888: zhi la dkar gsum rgyas 'bru'i tshogs //
NG0200:4889: dbang la sha chang dug khrag drag / phrin las gzhung bsrang tshogs mchod bya //
NG0200:4890: me yi lha bskyed mchod bstod bya //
NG0200:4891: phrin las gang bsgrub dang sbyar te //
NG0200:4892: lto bar yongs rdzogs lha bskyed de //
NG0200:4893: ye shes bkug bstim rten mchod rjes //
NG0200:4894: bkra shis bu tshas me spar te //
NG0200:4895: sbyin bsreg rdzogs byas las sngags ni //
NG0200:4896: rtsa sngags dag la 'di sbyar bskul //
NG0200:4900: las bzhi'i 'dod gsol dang bcas bsreg / zhi rgyas dbang drag gang bsam 'grub //
NG0200:4901: ye shes sems gshegs dam tshig bsdu //
NG0200:4902: rjes su las bzhi'i bro bzhi brdung *//
NG0200:4904: ba rlung chu mnan pa sogs //
NG0200:4905: so so'i las kyi dmigs dang bcas //
NG0200:4906: me yis las kun myur du 'grub //
NG0200:4908: dpal gsang ba 'dus pa rgyud kyi rgyal po las /
NG0200:4909: las bzhi sbyin bsreg yongs su bstan pa'i le'u ste
NG0200:4910: nyer dgu pa'o // // de nas yang 'dus pa'i
NG0200:4911: 'khor rnams kyis mgrin gcig tu ston pa kun tu
NG0200:4912: bzang po dpal che mchog he ru ka la gsol
NG0200:4914: thams cad ston pa kun tu bzang *//
NG0200:4915: thugs rje che mchog he ru ka / las rnams rjes bstan dgra bgegs gzir //
NG0200:4916: dpal chen rol pa'i bro rnams gang *//
NG0200:4917: de skad gsol pas bka' stsal pa //
NG0200:4918: gzir mnan bro yi las sbyor ni //
NG0200:4919: dgra bgegs dam sri gnan gzir te //
NG0200:4921: dpal gyi chas kyis rab tu brgyan //
NG0200:4922: yongs rdzogs lha yi nga rgyal bskyed //
NG0200:4923: lag pa lu gu rgyud du sbrel //
NG0200:4924: rkang stabs rdo rje'i 'gros su bya //
NG0200:4925: dpa' brjid rngam pa'i hum sgra sgrog / glu yis spyan drang bros gzir gnan //
NG0200:4926: phrin las rnam bzhi dmigs bsal bsgrub //
NG0200:4927: dang po glu yis spyan drang te //
NG0200:4928: hum zhi khro yongs rdzogs dkyil 'khor du //
NG0200:4929: dpal chen che mchog sku sprul nas //
NG0200:4930: mkha' 'gro'i tshogs dang rol pa ni //
NG0200:4931: thabs shes gnyis su med par sbyor //
NG0200:4933: khro bo khro mo'i sprin 'phros nas //
NG0200:4934: glu bro gar gyi thugs dam ste //
NG0200:4935: rgyun chad med par brtan par bya //
NG0200:4937: rgyal ba stong dang mnyam par sbyor //
NG0200:4938: glu ni tshangs pa'i dbyangs kyis 'dren //
NG0200:4939: ma dang mkha' 'gro'i thugs dam bskul //
NG0200:4940: tshig ni don dam rtogs pa'i tshig / chos sems gnyis su med par rtogs //
NG0200:4941: 'di ni glu bro gar gyi brda' //
NG0200:4942: gar ni khyab gdal chen po'i gar //
NG0200:4943: phyogs bcu'i zhing khams khyab par byed //
NG0200:4944: phyag rgya bsnol ba lu gu rgyud //
NG0200:4945: dus gsum rgyal ba zhi khro bskul //

NG0200:5786: om lam hum mum swa mam am pyam ha tram /

NG0200:5841: dpal chen sku gcig gsal bar dgod //
NG0200:5842: bskyed rdzogs gzhung bsrang 'dzab rdzogs rjes //

NG0200:5848: rtse gcig sems gzung yengs mi bya //

NG0200:5862: dgongs pa'i gzer ni zhi khro'i lha //

NG0200:5871: 'gyu dran rnam rtog bsam yas kyang *//

NG0200:5917: a yuhpha la sid+d+hi hum a /
